\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Luk t…ôm…ôte naoa u. Afin e ‚ÄúN…ôghat…ôn …ôku…ôk…®r r…ôha naoa u Luk‚Äù o n…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô Luk in pah.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* Luk t…ôm…ôte naoa u tatuw…®n k…ôm in kit, n…ôrg…®n u Teofilas, et…ôm kiti…ôh …ôm it…ôm Luk t…ôm…ôte naoa u ‚ÄúNamnus…ôn T…ôw…®r It…ôm Luk T…ôm…ôte‚Äù tatuw…®n k…ôm in. N…ôr…®g u, n…®p…ôt…®n t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ômim it…ôm tokeike Uhg…®n.‚Äù Luk t…ôm…ôte naoa u tatuw…®n k…ôm suah u, m…ôto in t…®tun m…ôm…ô Iaihlu…ô tep…ôt okotafin m…®n.  
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* Naoa m…®n r…ôha Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r koat…ôghat-in n…ômeg…ôh…ôn ne n…®m…®s…ôn r…ôha Iesu. Naoa u tat…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô nim…ôfak t…ômahro m…ôtuoun. Naoa u m…ôs…®n tat…ôghat-in t…ôp…ôt e w…ôk r…ôha Pita, k…ôn m…ôs…®n m…®n tat…ôghat-in n…ômeg…ôh…ôn ne w…ôk r…ôha Pol.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Luk t…ôm…ôte naoa u mat…ôn m…ôm…ô nim…ôfak t…ômahro min nulan m…ôtuoun, k…ôn otahro min nulan nim…ôfak otat…ôwi…ô. K…ôn e naoa u, kitat okotehm m…ôm…ô i…ôfak m…®n okotahruhalp…®n n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm net…ôm Isrel ne net…ôm Iaihlu…ô m…®n it…ôm kotolkeike m…ôm…ô okot…®tun n…ôuk…ôt…® nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhalat. E naoa u, kot…ôplan m…ôm…ô kapman r…ôha Rom tat…ôto n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Pol. K…ôn mat…ôplan m…ôm…ô Luk ne Pol kiolkeike m…ôm…ô net…ômim rafin it…ôm Rom tat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô elat, ilat okot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e Iesu.  
\c 1  
\s1 Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa  //  Narm…®n r…ôhan  
\m
\v 1 Teofilas, e r…ôhak naoa it…ôm em…ôte aup…ôn, em…ôte nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm Iesu t…ômatol ne mat…ôg…ôtun net…ômim lan.\x - \xo 1:1 \xt Luk 1:3 \x*  
\v 2 Naoa …ôh tat…ôn-iar…ôp nian Iesu t…ôm…ôtuoun r…ôhan w…ôk m…ôtoarus Uhg…®n t…ôm…®l…ôs matuw…®n e Nego e Neai. M…ôto aup…ôn, t…ôm…ôsuw…®n…ôn …ôh e Nego e Neai, Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôtasitu lan m…ôm…ô ot…ôg…ôtun r…ôhan aposol\f + \fr 1:2 \ft ‚ÄúAposol‚Äù in suah kit it…ôm Iesu Kristo t…ômahl-ipa o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn. Nian nakotafin n…ôghat…ôn …ôh ‚Äúaposol‚Äù e naoa u, n…®p…ôt…®n t…ôn m…ôm…ô net…ômim tuelef r…ôha Iesu u k…ômotaliw…ôk ilat min. K…ôn e naoa u, Pol t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô in m…®n aposol kit r…ôha Iesu, m…ôto in t…ôm…ôsaliw…ôk…ôn ilat net…ômim tuelef m…®n …ôh. Naoa …ôh, in tat…ôghat tep…ôt e aposol mil, Pita ne Pol.\f* m…®n.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Mak 16:19; Luk 24:49-51 \x*  
\v 3 E nian t…ôm…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn, nian tep…ôt tatuwa olat k…ôn ilat kot…ôplan in e nian kiti…ôh kiti…ôh e nian foti, k…ôn matol …ôp in k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô okot…®tun m…ôm…ô in t…ôm…ômeg…ôh pahrien e n…®m…®s…ôn. K…ôn e nian m…®n …ôh, t…ômat…ôg…ôtun ilat e n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 1:3 \xt Luk 24:36-49; W…ôk 10:41 \x*  
\v 4 Nian Iesu t…ôm…ôtat…®g …ôh ilat min ilat, in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn n…ôghaten kit k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômat on…ôsotaup…ôn…ôn motiet u e Jerusalem. On…ôkot…ôk…ôike k…ôtat…®g mot…ôtoarus on…ôkotos Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n, u r…ôhak tata t…®n…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat, tahmen m…®n m…ôm…ô inu io iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat.\x - \xo 1:4 \xt Luk 24:49; Jon 14:16-17; W…ôk 2:33 \x*  
\v 5 Aup…ôn Jon t…ômatol baptais e net…ômim e n…ôhau, m…ôto ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn, Uhg…®n in otol baptais et…ômat e Narm…®n R…ôhan.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:5 \xt Mat 3:11 \x*   
\s1 Uhg…®n t…ôm…®l…ôs Iesu muw…®n e Nego e Neai  
\p
\v 6 E nian m…®n …ôh, it…ôm aposol m…®n k…ômotat…®g ilat Iesu, k…ômot…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, t…®nuwa e nian …ôtuat…®p …ôh-roiu m…ôm…ô ik on…ôkol kitat net…ôm Isrel okot…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô m…®n e n…®t…ôn m…®n r…ôhatat, o k…ôp?‚Äù\x - \xo 1:6 \xt Luk 24:21 \x*  
\v 7 M…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúE nian m…®n r…ôha nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh, Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôhluaig-in ot…ômat, okol it…ômat n…ôsot…®tun…ôn. R…ôhak tata p…®s…®n …ôm, in t…®n…®t…ôpun r…ôk…®s e r…ôhan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt Mak 13:32 \x*  
\v 8 M…ôto e nian Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n otuwa mat…®g et…ômat, it…ômat on…ôkotos n…ôsan…ôn…ôn. K…ôn it…ômat onokot…ôk…ôike motuw…®n mot…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn …ôp…ôh Jerusalem, ne ik…®n m…®n …ôp…ôh Jutia, ne Sameria, k…ôn ne ik…®n m…®n rafin e n…ôtueint…ôn.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:8 \xt Mat 28:19; Luk 24:48 \x*   
\p
\v 9 Nian t…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s …ôm n…ôghat…ôn …ôh k…ôm ilat, k…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s in t…®n…ôr matuw…®n e neai. Nian ilat k…ômoat…ôplan, k…ôn napu…ô kit t…ômuwa malpin, k…ôn ilat k…ôm…ôsot…ôplan m…®n…ôn.  
\v 10 Nian k…ômot…®tagp…ôr …ôh e neai moateg…ôs-in, roiu ag…®n-…ôh, suah mil k…ôiu k…ômian e nat…®mnat ru…ôn k…ômuet-ar…ôpa mu…ôtul ilug…®n elat,  
\v 11 k…ôn mu…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Net…ôm Kalili! ?T…ôhrol n…ôkoat…ôtul ik…®n-u moat…ôtagp…ôr n…ôpo lan e napu…ô? Iesu …ôh it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s ot…ômat m…®l…ôs m…ôr matuw…®n e neai, in ot…ôpan…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n tahmen-p…ôn …ôm e it…ôm …ôh, it…ôm t…ôr matuw…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:11 \xt Mat 26:64; Luk 21:27 \x*   
\s1 Aposol m…®n  
\p
\v 12 K…ôn aposol m…®n k…ômotiet e n…®tot u kat…ôn m…ôm…ô, N…®tot R…ôha N…®g U Olif, mot…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn Jerusalem it…ôm s…ôn…ôm…ô in is…ôu p…®k, in iu…ôhk…®r …ôm.\x - \xo 1:12 \xt Luk 24:50-53 \x*  
\v 13 Nian k…ômotiet-ar…ôp…ôn Jerusalem, k…ômotuw…®n e n…®p…ôgnoa nim…ô kit …ôp…ôh il…®s lan it…ôm koatat…®g ik…®n. Aposol m…®n …ôh, n…ôrg…®lat u Pita ne Jon ne Jemes ne Antru, k…ôn Filip ne Tomas, k…ôn Patolomiu ne Matiu, k…ôn Jemes n…ôt…® Alfeas, k…ôn Saimon Selot,\f + \fr 1:13 \ft ∆èplan-tu futnot e Mat 10:4.\f* k…ôn Jutas n…ôt…® Jemes.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Mat 10:2-4 \x*  
\v 14 Net…ôm m…®n …ôh ne n…®p…®tan m…®n, ne Meri u mama r…ôha Iesu, ne pia Iesu m…®n, ilat koatuwa moat…ôfak kiti…ôh nian tep…ôt.   
\s1 Et…ômim it…ôm otos n…ôme Jutas  
\p
\v 15 Nian neen t…®nuwa m…®nuw…®n r…ôk…®s, k…ôn net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô e Iesu k…ômotuwa kiti…ôh. Ilat tep…ôt, tahmen e wan-hanr…®t-tuente ilat rafin. K…ôn Pita t…ôm…ôtul mat…ôghat k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô,  
\v 16 ‚ÄúPiak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n. N…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n ot…ôk…ôike muwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn lan, it…ôm nuw…ôh aup…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm Kig Tef…®t, k…ôn Kig Tef…®t t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp suah u Jutas m…ôm…ô in otit net…ômim motuw…®n kask…ôl…®m Iesu. K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn …ôh t…®nuwa …ôh-roiu m…®nol n…®pahrien…ôn lan.\x - \xo 1:16 \xt Sam 41:9 \x*  
\v 17 Jutas kitat min kiti…ôh …ôm. K…ôn in r…ôhan …ôh-ik…®n w…ôk it…ôm t…ômatol m…ôtasitu etat.‚Äù   
\p
\v 18 (Jutas u inu t…ômos-n…ômt…®n n…ôpt…ôn kit e m…ôni u t…ômos e nol…ôn rat it…ôm t…ômol. E n…ôpt…ôn …ôh, t…ômiet morin k…ôn k…ôhap n…ôrp…®n n…®sgan tiet.\x - \xo 1:18 \xt Mat 27:3-8 \x*  
\v 19 K…ôn net…ôm Jerusalem k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, k…ômotaun-in n…ôpt…ôn …ôh e n…ôghat…ôn ik…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúAkeltama,‚Äù n…®p…ôt…®n u m…ôm…ô N…ôpt…ôn e N…®ta.)   
\p
\v 20 K…ôn Pita t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúE Naoa R…ôha Napu…ôn M…®n, n…ôghat…ôn kit tat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄòT…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô r…ôhan nim…ô tat…ôtul …ôpnap…®n …ôm, okol et…ômim kit t…ôsat…®g…ôn ik…®n.‚Äô\x - \xo 1:20 \xt Sam 69:25; 109:8 \x*  
\p ‚ÄúK…ôn n…ôghat…ôn kit m…®n tat…ôn min-nulan m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄòT…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô et…ôm p…®s…®n kit otuwa mos n…ômeen mol w…ôk r…ôhan.‚Äô   
\p
\v 21-22 ‚ÄúK…ôn tol n…ôhlan, okot…ôk…ôike k…®lesip…ôr suah kit it…ôm t…ômehm e n…®gan…ômt…®n n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha Iesu e n…®m…®s…ôn, k…ôn in otuwa m…®n mehm kitat m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-iar…ôp Iesu m…ôm…ô in I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat. Suah u, in suah kit it…ôm kitat min k…ômoatan aup…ôn e nian m…®n u it…ôm I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu t…ôm…ôtaliw…ôk lan. Suah un in suah kit it…ôm t…ôm…ôtat…®g nian Jon t…ômat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha nol…ôn baptais et…ôm, muwa m…ôtoarus-p…ôn nian it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ir…ôk…®s Iesu o kitat m…®l…ôs m…ôr muw…®n e Nego e Neai.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:21-22 \xt Mak 1:9; 16:19; Jon 15:27 \x*   
\p
\v 23 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôrg…® et…ômim k…ôiu, kit n…ôrg…®n u Josep u nian neen k…ôtaun-in m…ôm…ô Pasapas o Jastas, k…ôn kit m…®n, n…ôrg…®n u Matias.  
\v 24 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôfak mot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, ik n…ôk…®tun n…®ki net…ômim rafin. Ik asitu et…®mat m…ôm…ô suah mil u, in p…ôhru…ôn ik n…®n…ôm…®t…ôpun r…ôk…®s  
\v 25 m…ôm…ô otask…ôl…®m w…ôk u r…ôha aposol it…ôm Jutas t…ômap…ôs m…ôm…ô otuw…®n e suat…®p it…ôm t…ôrat, iman …ôtuat…®p ik…®n.‚Äù  
\v 26 Nian k…ômot…ôfak r…ôk…®s, ilat k…ômoturin k…ôpiel neen, kotahmen e tais, m…ôm…ô ot…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô pah otos w…ôk …ôh, k…ôn n…ôrg…® Matias t…ômiet. K…ôn ilat k…ômot…®l…ôs-ip…ôn Matias m…ôm…ô in aposol kit, k…ôn roiu t…®nol m…®n tuelef aposol ilat rafin.   
\c 2  
\s1 Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômuwa e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhalat  
\m
\v 1 E nian r…ôha Pentekos,\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Pentekos: ∆èplan e tiksonari.\f* lafet kit r…ôha noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel, net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô e Iesu k…ômotuwa kiti…ôh.\x - \xo 2:1 \xt Lev 23:15-21; Dut 16:9-11 \x*  
\v 2 K…ôn roiu ag…®n m…®n, k…ômot…ôto nat kit t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôr e neai tahmen e n…®m…ôtag asol kit tatelel nat, k…ôn nat …ôh k…ômot…ôto t…ômuwa m…ôr rafin e n…®p…ôgnoa nim…ô it…ôm koat…ôp…ôl…ôh ik…®n.  
\v 3 K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôplan nat kit tahmen e n…®g…ôm t…ômu…ôp. K…ôn l…ôpl…ôpin n…®g…ôm m…®n …ôh, k…ômotiw…®g motan ahmen-in net…ômim rafin it…ôm koat…ôp…ôl…ôh …ôh im…ô.\x - \xo 2:3 \xt Mat 3:11 \x*  
\v 4 K…ôn ilat rafin, Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômuwa m…ôrioah m…ôtat…®g elat, k…ôn m…®nos-ip…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn k…ôm ilat, mol ilat k…®noat…ôghat e n…ôghat…ôn ik p…®s…®n m…®n.\x - \xo 2:4 \xt Mak 16:17; W…ôk 4:31; 10:44-46; 19:6 \x*   
\p
\v 5 K…ôn noanol m…®n neen …ôh-ik…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel it…ôm koat…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n. Ilat k…ômot…®s…®-p…ôn ik p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n m…ôto kotat…®g Jerusalem.  
\v 6 Nian ilat k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôh, net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômotuwa. K…ôn ilat k…ômotaut p…®k m…ôto-inu k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhalat it…ôm net…ôm m…®n …ôh koat…ôn.  
\v 7 K…ômotaut p…®k ag…®n k…ôn mot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! ?Net…ôm Kalili …ôm …ôh koat…ôghat, o k…ôp?  
\v 8 ?Tahro kitat rafin koat…ôto r…ôhatat n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm ilat koat…ôn?  
\v 9-11 Kitat u net…ôm ik p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n tep…ôt. Ik…®n-u net…ôm Patia …ôh-ik…®n, ne net…ôm Metia, ne net…ôm Elam, ne net…ôm Mesopotemia, ne net…ôm Jutia, ne net…ôm Kapatosia, ne net…ôm Pontas, ne net…ôm Esia, ne net…ôm Fritia, ne net…ôm Pamfilia, ne net…ôm Ijip, ne net…ôm Lipia e n…®kal…®n-p…ôn …ôh Saerin ik…®n, ne net…ôm Rom, neen noanol …ôtuat…®p r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, neen net…ôm p…®s…®n m…ôto koat…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n, ne net…ôm Krit, ne net…ôm Arepia. M…ôto kitat rafin k…ômot…ôto ilat koat…ôn nat asol it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômol e n…ôghat…ôn ik p…®s…®n m…®n r…ôhatat.‚Äù  
\v 12 Narm…®lat t…ômiw…®g p…®k, rehalat-kap…ô t…ôm…®k…ô, k…ôn k…ômoat…ôtap…ôh olat m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! ?Naka u tol nulan?‚Äù   
\p
\v 13 M…ôto neen k…ômotalah-…ômnu ilat, mot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNat koatap…®s …ôp…ôh.‚Äù   
\s1 Pita t…ôm…ôghat k…ôm net…ômim  
\p
\v 14 K…ôn Pita t…ôm…ôtul ilat lepen aposol m…®n, t…ômag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh mat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ômim m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômat rafin noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel ne net…ôm p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n u nakoatat…®g Jerusalem, ot…ôt…ôl…®g-in w…®r-tu io, p…ôs ekuhap…®k e n…®p…ôt…® nat …ôh k…ôm it…ômat.  
\v 15 It…ômat nakoat…ôn m…ôm…ô net…ôm m…®n u koatap…®s. M…ôto k…ôp, k…ôsotap…®s…ôn. Nain k…®lok …ôm …ôh-roiu laulaug…®n. ?K…ôn tahro ilat koatap…®s?\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Net…ôm …ôh k…ôsot…ôn…®m…ôn wain laulaug…®n, k…ôn et…ôm t…®k…ô it…ôm t…ôtap…®s laulaug…®n.\f*   
\p
\v 16 ‚ÄúM…ôto in tol nulan. Ien r…ôha Uhg…®n aup…ôn, n…ôrg…®n u Joel, t…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s nat u it…ôm it…ômat nakoat…ôplan. In t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\v 17 ‚ÄòUhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúE namnun nian m…®n, ekos-ip…ôn r…ôhak Narm…®n k…ôm net…ômim rafin. Ilat rafin okotos n…ôsan…ôn…ôn lan. Nen…ôt…®t…ômat m…®n, n…ôman ne n…®p…®tan, ilat okot…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhak it…ôm io iatos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat. Net…ôm alu…ô m…®n r…ôhat…ômat, Uhg…®n otos-ip…ôn nat kit tahmen e nap…®laiir…ôn k…ôm ilat. K…ôn nagu…®hl-agu…®hl m…®n r…ôhat…ômat okotap…®laiir e nap…®laiir…ôn p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n.  
\v 18 S…ôn…ôm…ô net…ôm-iasol m…®n …ôm, m…ôto n…ôman ne n…®p…®tan ilat nolw…ôk m…®n …ôm r…ôhak, k…ôn ekos-ip…ôn Narm…®n r…ôhak k…ôm ilat. K…ôn ilat okot…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhak it…ôm iatos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat.  
\v 19 Oekol nat p…®sp…®s m…®n …ôp…ôh e neai, ne n…ômt…ôtin p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n e n…®m…ôpt…ôn. On…ôkot…ôplan n…®ta ne n…®g…ôm ne n…ôhani…ôm okot…ôr motol napu…ô lan.  
\v 20 Aup…ôn, m…®tgar otapin…ôp k…ôn m…ôw…®g otasi…ô tahmen e n…®ta. K…ôn uaris…®g, Nian asol asol ag…®n r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô otuwa.  
\v 21 E nian …ôh, net…ômim rafin it…ôm okotaun-in N…ôrg…ôk, io ekosmeg…ôh ilat.‚Äù‚Äô\x - \xo 2:21 \xt Joel 2:28-32 \x*   
\p
