\v 60 K…ôn t…ômeiuaiu m…®sin nul…®n k…ôn mas…ôk …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, af…ôl nol…ôn rat it…ôm ilat koatol lak.‚Äù Nian t…ômol namnun r…ôhan n…ôfak…ôn, k…ôn r…ôhan nameg…ôn tiet.\x - \xo 7:60 \xt Luk 23:34 \x*   
\c 8  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn Sol tat…ôtul …ôm n…®kin t…ôtagien m…ôm…ô ilat k…ômotaht…®mnu Stipen.  
\s1 Sol t…ômoh net…ôm koat…ôfak  
\p M…ôtuoun e nian …ôh, n…ôrat…ôn asol k…®natol e nim…ôfak …ôp…ôh Jerusalem. K…ôn ilat k…ômotiet Jerusalem motag…®m-p…ôn Jutia ne Sameria, motap…ôs p…®s…®n …ôm aposol m…®n koatat…®g Jerusalem.  
