\v 3 M…ôto Sol t…ôm…ôtuoun m…®nat…ôr…ôk…®n-…ôr…ôk…®n nim…ôfak, matuw…®n e nim…ô m…®n matewk…ôkan-iar…ôp n…ôman ne n…®p…®tan it…ôm koat…ôfak, k…ôn mat…ômki-p…ôn ilat e kalapus.\x - \xo 8:3 \xt W…ôk 9:1,13; 22:4; 26:9-11 \x*   
