\p
\v 4 K…ôn net…ôm koat…ôfak it…ôm k…ômotiet Jerusalem moatag…®m, k…ômot…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n ik…®n m…®n rafin it…ôm ilat koatuw…®n ik…®n.  
\v 5 Filip t…ômuw…®n e taon kit r…ôha Sameria, k…ôn mat…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn r…ôha Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa.  
\v 6 Nian n…®manin net…ômim k…ômot…ôto Filip, k…ôn mot…ôplan nat p…®sp…®s m…®n it…ôm in tatol, ilat rafin k…ômotuwa iu…ôhk…®r kat…ôt…ôl…®g-in nat naka in tat…ôn.  
\v 7 Net…ômim tep…ôt narm…®n rat m…®n k…ômotiet elat. Nian narm…®n rat m…®n k…ômoatiet, k…ômotear…®g …ôf…ôm…ôh. K…ôn net…ômim tep…ôt it…ôm n…®p…ôt…®lat t…ôm…®m…®s, o it…ôm k…ôsotaliw…ôk…ôn, k…ômot…ôw…®r m…®n.  
\v 8 K…ôn net…ômim rafin e taon …ôh, ilat rafin koatagien.   
\s1 Saimon u t…ômol nat…®mnat e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha i…ôrm…®s m…®n  
\p
\v 9 K…ôn e taon …ôh, suah kit n…ôrg…®n u Saimon, in t…ômatol nat p…®sp…®s tep…ôt e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha i…ôrm…®s m…®n, k…ôn net…ômim rafin r…ôha Sameria, narm…®lat t…ômiw…®g ron. T…ômol nuw…ôh m…ôs…®n. In matos-ip…ôr at…®p in m…ôm…ô in et…ôm-iasol kit.  
\v 10 K…ôn net…ômim rafin, net…ôm-iasol m…ôtoarus-pa iolw…ôk m…®n …ôm, k…ômoat…ôtag-p…ôn p…®k ron k…ôn moat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSuah u in uhg…®n kit u n…ôrg…®n u Uhg…®n It…ôm R…ôhan N…ôsan…ôn…ôn Il…®s.‚Äù  
\v 11 K…ômoat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn in nuw…ôh m…ôs…®n m…ôto-inu narm…®lat tatiw…®g o nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm in tatol.  
\v 12 M…ôto nian net…ômim k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm Filip tat…ôn-iar…ôp e namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n ne n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Iesu Kristo, k…ômot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn lan, k…ôn k…ômol baptais elat, n…ôman ne n…®p…®tan.  
\v 13 Suah m…®n u Saimon, t…ôm…ôn m…®n n…®pahrien…ôn e Iesu, k…ôn kol baptais m…®n lan. K…ôn in tat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn Filip ik…®n m…®n rafin. Narm…®n tatiw…®g o nat p…®sp…®s m…®n ne n…ômt…ôtin m…®n it…ôm in tat…ôplan Filip tatol.   
\p
\v 14 Nian aposol m…®n …ôp…ôh Jerusalem k…ômot…ôto m…ôm…ô net…ôm Sameria k…®notahat…ôt…ô e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn k…ômotahl-ip…ôn Pita ne Jon m…ôm…ô okian olat.  
\v 15 Nian ilau k…ômian muet-ar…ôp…ôn olat, k…ômu…ôfak olat m…ôm…ô Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n ot…ôrioah m…ôtat…®g elat,  
\v 16 m…ôto-inu k…ômol baptais …ôm elat e n…ôrg…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu, m…ôto Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôs…ôrioah…ôn …ôh e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhalat.  
\v 17 K…ôn Pita ne Jon k…ômu…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nelm…®lau elat mu…ôfak elat, k…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôrioah m…ôtat…®g elat.\x - \xo 8:17 \xt W…ôk 19:6 \x*   
\p
\v 18 Nian Saimon t…ôm…ôplan m…ôm…ô Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n tatuw…®n e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha net…ômim nian aposol mil katu…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nelm…®lau elat matu…ôfak elat, k…ôn in t…ôm…ômki-ar…ôp m…ôni m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilau,  
\v 19 k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilau m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIos-ipa m…®n n…ôsan…ôn…ôn u k…ôm io m…ôm…ô nian iak…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nelm…ôk e net…ômim, k…ôn ilat kot…®tun nos…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 20 M…ôto Pita t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ik ne r…ôham m…ôni onakian e n…®g…ôm asol! M…ôto-inu ik n…®kim t…ôht m…ôm…ô n…ôk…®tun nos-n…ômt…®n…ôn e m…ôni nat u it…ôm Uhg…®n tatos-ip…ôn …ôm k…ôm net…ômim.  
\v 21 Okol ik n…ôsol…ôn w…ôk u m…ôs…®n ne, m…ôto-inu r…ôham n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n.  
\v 22 ∆èuhlin ik e r…ôham nol…ôn rat m…®n k…ôn m…ôfak-p…ôn k…ôm I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, m…ôta in taf…ôl r…ôk…®s r…ôham nol…ôn rat m…®n it…ôm n…®kim tatu…ôhl-u…ôhl ilat.  
\v 23 Em…ôplan m…ôm…ô nian rafin net…ôhak…ôn t…ômol r…ôham n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn tuw…®n ik p…®s…®n, k…ôn nol…ôn rat …ôh t…ôm…ôlis ik ti…ôk…®s.‚Äù   
\p
\v 24 K…ôn Saimon t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Awi! U…ôfak-p…ôn k…ôm I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô ron io m…ôm…ô nat…®mnat it…ôm it…ôlau n…ômu…ôn, kit ot…ôsuwam…ôn ron io.‚Äù   
\p
\v 25 Nian ilau k…ômu…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô ne nat…®mnat it…ôm in t…ômol, k…ôn ilau k…ômiaiet Sameria m…ôtian Jerusalem, mu…ôtul …ôgmag…®m e latu…ônu m…®n r…ôha Sameria matu…ôn-iar…ôp m…®n namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.   
\s1 Filip t…ôm…ôghat k…ôm et…ôm Itiopia kit  
\p
\v 26 K…ôn nagelo kit r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Filip m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆èsou pis muw…®n e suat…®p tat…®s…®-p…ôn Jerusalem matuw…®n Kasa.‚Äù (Suat…®p …ôh tat…ôm…ôhl …ôp…ôh ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n.)\fig |alt="Phillip approaching official‚Äôs chariot" src="LB00331B.TIF" size="col" loc="Act 8:26-30" ref="W…ôk 8:26" \fig*  
\v 27 K…ôn in t…ômatuw…®n …ômun m…ôplan et…ôm Itiopia kit e suat…®p. Suah …ôh in et…ôm-iasol kit r…ôha kwin r…ôha net…ôm Itiopia.\f + \fr 8:27 \ft N…ôghat…ôn Kris …ôtuat…®p tat…ôn m…ôm…ô in suah kit it…ôm k…ômate. E nian …ôh, ok…ôm…ô suah kit tatol w…ôk nian rafin iu…ôhk…®r e Kwin kit, k…ôn okate m…ôm…ô ot…ôsit…ôn Kwin.\f* K…ôn in tat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e m…ôni rafin r…ôha kwin. Suah u t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn Jerusalem e n…ôfak…ôn,  
\v 28 k…ôn m…®n…®t…ôl…®g matuw…®n iman ik…®n. K…ôn in tat…ôp…ôl…ôh-p…ôr e nat kit kat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äúkat‚Äù it…ôm hos tatiuw. K…ôn m…ôtafin naoa it…ôm ien r…ôha Uhg…®n Aesea t…ôm…ôte.  
\v 29 K…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Filip m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUw…®n maliw…ôk iu…ôhk…®r o kat …ôh.‚Äù   
\p
\v 30 K…ôn Filip t…ômaiu muw…®n iu…ôhk…®r ron, m…ôto suah u t…ôtafin naoa it…ôm ien r…ôha Uhg…®n Aesea t…ôm…ôte. K…ôn t…ôm…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?N…ôk…®tun n…®p…ôt…® nat un nakatafin, o k…ôp?‚Äù   
\p
\v 31 K…ôn suah un t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Filip m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ekahro m…®tun? M…ôto-inu suah kit t…®k…ô it…ôm otuhap…®k n…®p…ôt…® n…ôghat…ôn u k…ôm io.‚Äù K…ôn in m…ôtap…ôh m…ôm…ô Filip ot…ôr muw…®n ilau min mu…ôp…ôl…ôh.  
\v 32 In t…ôm…ôtafin n…ôghat…ôn u e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, tat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…ômit tahmen e sipsip kan m…ôm…ô okohamnu.  
\q1 K…ôn tahmen e n…ôt…® sipsip, t…ôs…ôghat…ôn nian kat…ôte noanun,  
\q1 K…ôn in t…ôm…ôpnap…®n …ôm, m…ôs…ôghat…ôn.   
\q1
\v 33 K…ômol aul…®s in, k…ôn nian k…ômakil e kot, k…®sakil …ôtuat…®p…ôn.  
\q1 Nian k…ômotohamnu, in et…ôm alu…ô …ôm kit, it…ôm n…ôt…®n t…®k…ô.‚Äù\x - \xo 8:33 \xt Aes 53:7-8\x*   
\p
\v 34 K…ôn suah u t…ôm…ôtap…ôh o Filip m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Karm…ô Aesea t…ômat…ôghat at…®p in, o et…ôm p…®s…®n kit?‚Äù  
\v 35 K…ôn Filip t…ôm…ôtuoun e n…ôghat…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm it…ôm t…ôm…ôtafin, mat…ôn-ip…ôn namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha Iesu.   
\p
\v 36 Nian k…ômatian e suat…®p muea ik…®n kit n…ôhau …ôh-ik…®n, k…ôn suah un t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Filip m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!∆èplan-tu! N…ôhau kit …ôp…ôh. ?Tahro? ?P…ôs nakol baptais lak lan?‚Äù\f + \fr 8:36 \ft E kopi oas m…®n neen r…ôha Niutesteman it…ôm k…ôm…ôte e n…ôghat…ôn Kris aup…ôn, n…ôghat…ôn u e ves 37, k…ôm…ôs…ôte…ôn. M…ôto kat…ôplan ves 37 e naoa neen uaris…®g, k…ôn in tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…ôn Filip t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòOk…ôm…ô nakat…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e Iesu e n…®kim rafin, ek…®tun nol…ôn baptais lam.‚Äô K…ôn t…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIo iat…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e Iesu, m…ôm…ô in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n pahrien.‚Äô‚Äù\f*\x - \xo 8:36 \xt W…ôk 10:47 \x*   
\p
\v 38 K…ôn t…ôm…ôn-i…ôhau kat m…ôm…ô ot…ôtul, k…ôn ilau k…ôr…ôn k…ômian …ôp…ôh l…ôhau e n…ôhau, k…ôn Filip tol baptais lan.  
\v 39 Nian k…ômu…ôr e n…ôhau muea il…®s, Narm…®n r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s Filip. K…ôn suah un t…ôm…®s…ôplan m…®n…ôn, m…ôto t…ôm…®t…ôl…®g matuw…®n iman ik…®n e nagien…ôn asol e n…®kin.  
\v 40 M…ôto Filip t…ômaut …ôm, m…ôplan tat…ôtul …ôp…ôh e n…®t…ôn p…ôhap ik…®n …ôp…ôh Astot. K…ôn in t…ômatuw…®n …ôp…ôh e taon m…®n mat…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha Iesu m…ôtoarus in t…ômiet-p…ôn …ôp…ôh Sisaria.\x - \xo 8:40 \xt W…ôk 21:8 \x*   
\c 9  
\s1 Sol t…ôm…ôplan Iesu e suat…®p r…ôha Tamaskes  
\r (W…ôk 22:6-16; 26:12-18)  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn e nian …ôh, Sol t…ômat…ôghat …ôskas…®k mat…ôn-i…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otohamnu net…ômim r…ôha Iesu. In t…ômuw…®n m…ôplan pris asol ag…®n\x - \xo 9:1 \xt W…ôk 8:3 \x*  
\v 2 m…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô ot…ôte naoa kit k…ôm nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel …ôp…ôh Tamaskes, m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô ot…ôplan kit tat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn Suat…®p R…ôha Iesu, nat …ôpnap…®n i…ôrman o p…ôtan, otask…ôl…®m ilat m…ôlis ilat m…ôm…®k ilat muw…®n e kalapus …ôp…ôh Jerusalem.   
\p
\v 3 Nian Sol t…ômuwa iu…ôhk…®r o Tamaskes, roiu ag…®n m…®n n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn kit t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôr e neai tatu…ôp tahmen e n…®p…®t…ôn muwa masi…ôg…ôp…®n in ne ik…®n m…®n t…®t…ôlau lan.  
\v 4 K…ôn in t…ômiet morin e n…ôpt…ôn, k…ôn m…ôto n…ôwia suah kit tat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Sol! !Sol! ?Tahro natol n…ôrat…ôn k…ôm io?‚Äù   
\p
\v 5 K…ôn Sol t…ôtap…ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ik pah, I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô?‚Äù K…ôn n…ôwia suah un t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo Iesu it…ôm ik natol t…ôrat k…ôm io.  
\v 6 M…ôto roiu …ôtul muw…®n …ôp…ôh e taon. Ik…®n …ôh, suah kit …ôh-ik…®n ot…ôpan…ôn-ip…®n…ô m…ôm…ô nat naka on…ôkol.‚Äù  
\v 7 K…ôn net…ômim it…ôm koatuaris…®g-in Sol, k…ômotaut k…ôtul k…ôs…ôghat…ôn, k…ômot…ôto …ôm n…ôwia suah un, m…ôto k…ôsot…ôplan…ôn.  
\v 8 K…ôn Sol t…ôtul, m…ôto n…®gan…ômt…®n t…®noapoap, t…®n…ôruru nehm…ôn nat. K…ôn k…ômotos …ôm nelm…®n motit motuw…®n Tamaskes.  
\v 9 T…ômos nian k…®s…®l t…ôm…®sehm…ôn nat, k…ôn t…ôm…ôsagw…ôn…ôn k…ôn m…ôs…ôn…®m…ôn n…ôhau ne.   
\p
\v 10 ∆èp…ôh e Tamaskes, et…ôm r…ôha Iesu kit …ôh-ik…®n, n…ôrg…®n u Ananaeas. I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ômaun-in e nat kit tahmen e nap…®laiir…ôn, k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ananaeas!‚Äù K…ôn in tag…ôt m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, io …ôp…ôh.‚Äù   
\p
\v 11 K…ôn I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUw…®n …ôh e nim…ô r…ôha Jutas e suat…®p asol it…ôm kat…ôn m…ôm…ô T…ôtuat…®p, k…ôn m…ôtap…ôh o et…ômim kit, et…ôm Tasas, n…ôrg…®n u Sol. In tat…ôghat roiu k…ôm Uhg…®n e n…ôfak…ôn,  
\v 12 k…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn nap…®laiir…ôn kit, k…ôn t…ôm…ôplan et…ômim kit, n…ôrg…®n u Ananaeas, t…ômuwa m…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nelm…®n lan m…ôm…ô n…®gan…ômt…®n ot…ôw…®r m…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 13 M…ôto Ananaeas t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, em…ôto n…ôn…ôn tep…ôt e suah …ôh e r…ôhan nol…ôn rat m…®n it…ôm tatol e net…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô lam …ôp…ôh Jerusalem.  
\v 14 K…ôn in t…ômuwa ik…®n-u e n…ôrg…® pris asol m…®n m…ôm…ô otask…ôl…®m, m…ôlis net…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô lam.‚Äù   
\p
\v 15 M…ôto I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôm…ôn k…ôm Ananaeas m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Uw…®n! M…ôto-inu suah u in r…ôhak et…ômim it…ôm en…ômaun-in r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôrg…ôk k…ôm net…ôm Iaihlu…ô u s…ôn…ôm…ô net…ôm Isrel, ne r…ôhalat kig m…®n, ne net…ôm Isrel.\x - \xo 9:15 \xt W…ôk 26:2,6; 27:24; Rom 1:5 \x*  
\v 16 K…ôn io epan…ôg…ôtun in m…ôm…ô otos nahm…ô…ôn o n…ôrg…ôk.‚Äù\x - \xo 9:16 \xt 2 Kor 11:23-28 \x*   
\p
\v 17 K…ôn Ananaeas t…ômuw…®n latu…ônu muw…®n im…ô, k…ôn m…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nelm…®n e Sol, m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúPiak Sol. I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu it…ôm t…ômiet-ar…ôp ron ik e suat…®p nian n…ômoatuwa ik…®n-u, in t…ômahl-ipa io m…ôm…ô ik onakehm m…®n nat, k…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n ot…ôrioah m…ôtat…®g lam.‚Äù  
\v 18 Roiu ag…®n, nat kit tahmen e nuwil…®g…® n…ôm t…ômiet r…ôk…®s e n…®gan…ômt…® Sol, k…ôn in t…®naiir m…®n m…®natehm nat. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôtul m…®nataliw…ôk, k…ôn kol baptais lan m…ôm…ô in n…ômt…ôtin r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn.  
\v 19 K…ôn nian t…ômun nagw…ôn…ôn neen, k…ôn n…®p…ôt…®n t…ôm…ôsan…ôn m…®n.  
\s1 Sol t…®n…ôtuoun mat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôrg…® Iesu …ôp…ôh Tamaskes  
\p K…ôn Sol t…ômat…®g mos nian neen m…®n ilat net…ôm r…ôha Iesu …ôp…ôh Tamaskes.  
\v 20 T…ôm…ôtuoun m…®n …ôm e nian …ôh, mat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôrg…® Iesu …ôp…ôh e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, m…ôm…ô Iesu in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n pahrien.   
\p
\v 21 K…ôn net…ômim rafin it…ôm k…ômot…ôto in, k…ômotaut p…®k ron, k…ôn mot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! ?Suah u inu t…ômatol n…ôrat…ôn k…ôm net…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô e Iesu …ôp…ôh Jerusalem aup…ôn, o k…ôp? K…ôn in t…ômuwa ik…®n-u m…ôm…ô otask…ôl…®m ilat m…ôlis ilat m…ôm…®k muw…®n k…ôm pris asol m…®n. ?In …ôh, o k…ôp?‚Äù\x - \xo 9:21 \xt W…ôk 8:3 \x*   
\p
\v 22 K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm Sol tat…ôn-iar…ôp, in t…ôsan…ôn p…®k mapr…ôk…®s-in n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel it…ôm koatat…®g Tamaskes, k…ôn mat…ôg…ôtun w…®r m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa. K…ôn ilat k…®not…ôruru nat okot…ôn.\x - \xo 9:22 \xt W…ôk 18:28 \x*  
\v 23 Nian tep…ôt t…ômuwa muw…®n r…ôk…®s, k…ôn net…ôm Isrel neen k…ômoat…ôte anion noa kit m…ôm…ô okotohamnu Sol,  
\v 24 m…ôto Sol t…ôm…ôto noa anion r…ôhalat. K…ôn roiu e n…ôraui…ôg…ôn ne lap…®n m…®n, net…ôm Isrel kot…ôtlos…®g …ôp…ôh e nafilu…ô r…ôha fen…®s k…ômol e k…ôpiel m…ôm…ô okotohamnu Sol.\f + \fr 9:24 \ft E taon …ôh Tamaskes, tahmen e taon tep…ôt, aup…ôn aup…ôn k…ômol fen…®s asol e k…ôpiel t…®t…ôlau e taon.\f*  
\v 25 M…ôto in m…®n neen k…ômot…®l…ôs lap…®n motaii-p…ôn e k…ôt…®m asol kit it…ôm k…ôm…ôtu-p…ôn t…ôul…ô lan, motuw…®n mot…®l…ôs-iar…ôp e nakuhal e fen…®s. K…ôn in t…ômag…®m muw…®n Jerusalem.\x - \xo 9:25 \xt 2 Kor 11:32-33 \x*\fig |alt="Paul lowered in basket outside wall" src="LB00333B.TIF" size="col" loc="Act 9:25" ref="W…ôk 9:25" \fig*   
\s1 Sol …ôp…ôh Jerusalem  
\p
\v 26 Nian Sol t…ômuw…®n Jerusalem, t…ômalkut m…ôm…ô otuw…®n m…ôt…ôu-p…ôn net…ôm r…ôha Iesu, m…ôto ilat koat…ôgin, n…®kilat t…ôht m…ôm…ô tateiu…ô-in …ôm ilat m…ôm…ô in et…ôm r…ôha Iesu.\x - \xo 9:26 \xt Kal 1:17-19 \x*  
\v 27 M…ôto Panapas t…ômit muw…®n mit-ip…ôn k…ôm aposol m…®n, m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô t…ômahro nulan Sol t…ôm…ôplan I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu e suat…®p nian t…ômatuw…®n Tamaskes. K…ôn t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn m…®n k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôm…ôghat k…ôm Sol, k…ôn tahro nulan in t…®nat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôrg…® Iesu …ôp…ôh Tamaskes, m…ôs…ôg…®n…ôn.\x - \xo 9:27 \xt 1 Kor 9:1 \x*  
\v 28 K…ôn ilat Sol k…ômotat…®g k…ôn tatuw…®n ik…®n m…®n …ôp…ôh Jerusalem mat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôrg…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu m…ôs…ôg…®n…ôn.  
\v 29 K…ômot…ôghat ilat net…ôm Isrel it…ôm kot…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Kris, k…ômotoh ilat m…®n e n…ôghat…ôn. K…ôn k…®noatol m…ôm…ô okotohamnu Sol.  
\v 30 Nian in m…®n neen r…ôha nim…ôfak k…ômot…ôto, k…ômotuw…®n motit Sol motuw…®n …ôp…ôh l…ôhau iu…ôhk…®r o it…ôh…ôi e taon …ôh Sisaria, k…ôn motahl-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô otag…®m muw…®n …ôp…ôh is…ôu e taon …ôh Tasas.   
\p
\v 31 K…ôn net…ôm koat…ôfak …ôp…ôh Jutia, ne Kalili, ne Sameria k…ômotat…®g e n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn, et…ômim t…®k…ô it…ôm otol n…ôg…®n…ôn k…ôm ilat. K…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôtasitu elat mol ilat koat…ôtul …ôskas…®k, k…ôn ilat rafin koatat…®g kat…®siai-in I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. K…ôn ilat t…®natep…ôt.   
\s1 Pita t…ômol nelk…® Aeneas t…ôw…®r m…®n  
\p
\v 32 Pita t…ômaliw…ôk muw…®n ik…®n m…®n m…ôm…ô otuag net…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô e Iesu. E r…ôhan naliw…ôk…ôn, t…ômuw…®n m…ôplan net…ômim r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô …ôp…ôh e taon …ôh Lita.  
\v 33 T…ômuw…®n ik…®n …ôh m…ôplan suah kit n…ôrg…®n u Aeneas, n…®p…ôt…®n t…ôm…®m…®s t…®nos nup eit, t…ôsaliw…ôk…ôn m…ôtap…®l …ôm e r…ôhan pet.  
\v 34 K…ôn Pita t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúAeneas. Iesu Kristo tosmeg…ôh ik …ôh-roiu e r…ôham n…®m…®s…ôn. ∆ètul, maiu-aiu r…ôham n…®m…®tiw…®n.‚Äù K…ôn roiu ag…®n m…®n, Aeneas t…ôm…ôw…®r m…®n m…ôtul.  
\v 35 K…ôn net…ômim rafin Lita ne ik…®n m…®n rafin …ôp…ôh Saron k…ômot…ôplan suah u t…ômaliw…ôk m…ôtan, k…ôn ilat rafin k…®not…ôuhlin r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn k…ôn m…®noat…ôfak k…ôm I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.   
\s1 Pita t…ômol Tokas t…ômeg…ôh m…®n  
\p
\v 36 E taon kit Jopa, p…ôtan kit …ôh-ik…®n it…ôm in et…ôm r…ôha Iesu, n…ôrg…®n u Tapita, u n…®p…ôt…®n t…ôm…ô, ‚Äútia,‚Äù u in nat meg…ôh kit. E n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Kris, koat…ôn m…ôm…ô Tokas. P…ôtan u, nian rafin tatol t…ôw…®r k…ôm net…ômim k…ôn m…ôtasitu m…®n e ian-rat m…®n.\fig |alt="two story house with steps to the roof" src="LB00235B.TIF" size="col" loc="Act 9:36-39" ref="W…ôk 9:36" \fig*  
\v 37 M…ôto e nian …ôh, n…®m…®s…ôn kit t…ômol k…ôn t…®m…®s. K…ôn k…ômotau kol sen…®s k…ôm in, k…ôl…ôh…ôu e nim…ô …ôp…ôh il…®s ag…®n.  
\v 38 Ik…®n …ôh Lita iu…ôhk…®r …ôm o taon …ôh Jopa. K…ôn nian net…ôm r…ôha Iesu k…ômot…ôto m…ôm…ô Pita …ôp…ôh Lita, k…ômotahl-ip…ôn suah mil k…ôiu m…ôm…ô okian m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Otuwa u…ôhai …ôm-tu!‚Äù   
\p
\v 39 K…ôn Pita t…ôm…ôt…ôu-p…ôn ilau. Nian k…ôm…ôhalet-ar…ôpa latu…ônu, k…ômotit motuw…®n …ôp…ôh il…®s ag…®n. M…ôto n…ôutahl…®m…®s m…®n t…ôrioah …ôp…ôh ik…®n koatas…ôk ron, k…ôn k…ômoat…ôg…ôtun k…ôm Pita r…ôhalat nat…®mnat it…ôm p…ôtan …ôh t…ôm…ôhl nian t…ômat…ômeg…ôh.   
\p
\v 40 K…ôn Pita t…ômahl-iar…ôp rafin ilat, k…ôn meiuaiu m…®sin nul…®n mat…ôfak. K…ôn m…ôtag-p…ôn o p…ôtan …ôh t…ôm…®m…®s m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúTapita, …ôtul.‚Äù K…ôn p…ôtan apon t…ômaiir m…ôplan Pita, k…ôn m…ôtul mat…ôp…ôl…ôh.  
\v 41 K…ôn Pita t…ômea-p…ôn ron mask…ôl…®m miuw-p…ôr m…ôm…ô ot…ôtul e nelk…®n mil. K…ôn maun-in-p…ôn net…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô e Iesu ne n…ôutahl…®m…®s m…®n m…ôm…ô okotuwa im…ô, k…ôn mit-ip…ôn p…ôtan …ôh k…ôm ilat.  
\v 42 K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn e nat …ôh t…ômaiu m…®t…ôlau e taon …ôh Jopa. K…ôn tep…ôt k…ômot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu.  
\v 43 K…ôn Pita t…ômat…®g …ôh Jopa m…ôs…®n ilau suah kit n…ôrg…®n u Saimon it…ôm tatol nat…®mnat e nuwig…® kau.   
\c 10  
\s1 Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôghat k…ôm Konilias  
\m
\v 1 E taon Sisaria, suah kit …ôh-ik…®n n…ôrg…®n u Konilias. In et…ôm Rom, k…ôn in et…ôm-iasol r…ôha mopael ilat rafin wan-hanr…®t. K…ôn ilat koat…®s…®-p…ôn e ‚ÄúMopael r…ôha Itali.‚Äù  
\v 2 In et…ômim kit it…ôm tat…®siai-in Uhg…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, in ne r…ôhan m…®n ne r…ôhan iolw…ôk m…®n. In tatos-ip…ôn r…ôhan m…ôni tep…ôt k…ôm ian-rat m…®n, k…ôn mat…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n r…ôha Isrel nian rafin.  
\v 3 Nian kit …ômun e tri k…®lok ehnaip…ôn e nian tat…ôfak lan, t…ôm…ôplan nat kit tahmen e nap…®laiir…ôn. In t…ôm…ôplan w…®r nagelo kit r…ôha Uhg…®n tatuwa ron, k…ôn maun-in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Konilias!‚Äù  
\v 4 Nian n…®gan…ômt…® Konilias t…ôm…ôtul lan, in t…ôm…ôg…®n k…ôn m…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, tahro?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn nagelo t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUhg…®n t…®n…ôplan r…ôk…®s n…ôfak…ôn r…ôham ne n…ôw…®r…ôn it…ôm natol k…ôm ian-rat m…®n.  
\v 5 Ahl-ip…ôn net…ômim neen kotuw…®n …ôp…ôh Jopa, mot…®l…ôs suah kit motuwa, n…ôrg…®n u Saimon Pita.  
\v 6 In t…ôtat…®g ilau suah kit n…ôrg…®n u Saimon u tatol nat…®mnat e nuwig…® kau. R…ôhan nim…ô tat…ôtul iu…ôhk…®r o it…ôh…ôi.‚Äù   
\p
\v 7 Nian nagelo it…ôm t…ômat…ôghat k…ôm in t…ômag…®m, k…ôn Konilias t…ômaun-in r…ôhan iolw…ôk k…ôiu ne mopael kit it…ôm tatol w…ôk k…ôm in, k…ôn in et…ôm r…ôha n…ôfak…ôn.  
\v 8 In t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn rafin nat…®mnat it…ôm t…ôm…ôplan k…ôm il…ôhal, k…ôn mahl-ip…ôn il…ôhal m…ôm…ô ok…ôhaluw…®n Jopa.   
\s1 Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôghat k…ôm Pita e nap…®laiir…ôn  
\p
\v 9 K…ôn k…ôm…ôn law…®gin, nian m…®tgar t…®nalalin, k…ôn suah mil…ôhal …ôh k…ômat…ôhaluwa e suat…®p iu…ôhk…®r o taon …ôh Jopa, Pita t…ômuw…®n …ôp…ôh il…®s e n…ôtuei nim…ô it…ôm tepin-epin ik…®n m…ôm…ô ot…ôghat k…ôm Uhg…®n e n…ôfak…ôn.\fig |alt="Houses in city" src="HK00232B.TIF" size="span" loc="Act 10:9-20" ref="W…ôk 10:9" \fig*  
\v 10 M…ôto n…ôum…®s t…®nus, k…ôn nian k…ômatol …ôh n…®g…®n nagw…ôn…ôn, in taiir m…ôto t…ôm…ôplan nap…®laiir…ôn kit it…ôm Uhg…®n tatos-ipa.  
\v 11 E nap…®laiir…ôn …ôh, t…ôm…ôplan neai t…ômer…ôh, k…ôn nat kit tahmen e tapol…ôn asol k…ôtask…ôl…®m n…®p…ôgn…ômt…®n m…®n, k…ôn k…ôhlman-…ôhlman teiuaiu matuwa e n…ôpt…ôn.  
\v 12 E n…®p…ôg nat …ôh, t…ôm…ôplan nat meg…ôh p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n …ôh-ik…®n it…ôm kotaliw…ôk ne mot…ôkioah, ne m…ôn…®g p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n.  
\v 13 K…ôn n…ôwia suah kit t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúPita, …ôtul. Ohamnu neen mon.‚Äù   
\p
\v 14 M…ôto Pita t…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, k…ôp! E r…ôhak n…ômeg…ôh…ôn eson…ôn …ôh nat kit nulan it…ôm Lou r…ôham t…ôm…ôn-i…ôhau m…ôm…ô k…ôsun…ôn tamk…®m…®k e n…®gan…ômt…®m.‚Äù\x - \xo 10:14 \xt Lev 11:1-47; Esik 4:14 \x*   
\p
\v 15 K…ôn n…ôwia suah u t…ôm…ôghat m…®n k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆ès…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô nat kit tamk…®m…®k it…ôm io Uhg…®n iat…ôn m…ôm…ô t…ôw…®r …ôm, t…ôsamk…®m…®k…ôn.‚Äù\x - \xo 10:15 \xt Mak 7:15,19 \x*  
\v 16 K…ômu…ôghat o nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh mau k…®s…®l, k…ôn roiu ag…®n m…®n, tapol…ôn apon t…ôm…ôr muw…®n …ôp…ôh e neai.   
\s1 Pita t…ômos n…®p…ôt…® nap…®laiir…ôn  
\p
\v 17 K…ôn Pita n…®kin t…ômat…ôht p…®k m…ôm…ô ot…®tun n…®p…ôt…® nat …ôh tahmen e nap…®laiir…ôn it…ôm t…ôm…ôplan. M…ôto suah mil…ôhal un it…ôm Konilias t…ômahl…ôpis il…ôhal, k…ôm…ôhal…ôtap…ôh o nim…ô r…ôha Saimon, k…ôn m…®n…ôhaluwa m…®n…ôhal…ôplan. K…ôn m…®n…ôhaluw…®n m…ôt…ôhal…ôtul …ôp…ôh e nafilu…ô.  
\v 18 K…ôn m…ôhlaun …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! ?Suah kit u ik…®n-u n…ôrg…®n u Saimon Pita?‚Äù   
\p
\v 19 K…ôn nian Pita t…ôtalkut …ôh m…ôm…ô ot…®tun n…®p…ôt…® nat …ôh tahmen e nap…®laiir…ôn, k…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei, …ôto-tu! Suah mil…ôhal k…®s…®l …ôp…ôh kat…ôhaleg…ôs-in ik.  
\v 20 ∆ètul u…ôhai matite muw…®n m…ôplan il…ôhal. K…ôn m…ôs…ôg…®n…ôn o n…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn il…ôhal m…ôto-inu io emahl-ipa il…ôhal m…ôm…ô ok…ôhaluwa.‚Äù   
\p
\v 21 K…ôn Pita t…ômeiuaiu muw…®n m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm il…ôhal m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo u inu it…ôm it…ôm…ôhal nat…ôhaleg…ôs-in. ?Nak…ôhalolkeike io o naka?‚Äù   
\p
\v 22 K…ôn k…ôhal…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆èw…ôh. Et…ôm tat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e mopael m…®n, u Konilias, t…ômahl-ipa it…®m…ôhal m…ôm…ô ek…ôhaluwa. In suah kit it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôn in mat…ôfak m…®n k…ôm Uhg…®n. K…ôn noanol m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel koat…®siai-in p…®k. Nagelo kit r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô ik on…ôkuw…®n …ôh iman ik…®n, k…ôn mamnus n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm in p…ôs in ot…ôto.‚Äù  
\v 23 K…ôn Pita t…ômit il…ôhal motuw…®n im…ô m…ôm…ô ilat okotap…®l …ôh-ik…®n.  
\s1 Pita t…ômuw…®n e nim…ô r…ôha Konilias  
\p K…ôn k…ôm…ôn law…®gin, Pita t…ôm…ôt…ôu-p…ôn il…ôhal, k…ôn i…ôfak m…®n neen r…ôha Jopa, k…ômot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn ilat.  
\v 24 K…ôm…ôn law…®gin m…®n, k…ômotiet-ar…ôp…ôn …ôp…ôh Sisaria. Ik…®n …ôh Konilias t…ôm…ôtap…ôh o r…ôhan m…®n ne net…ômim neen m…ôm…ô okotuwa kat…ôsahgin Pita.  
\v 25 Nian Pita t…ômatuw…®n m…ôm…ô otuw…®n im…ô, k…ôn Konilias t…ômiet m…®sin nul…®n e nelk…® Pita ik…®n m…ôm…ô ot…ôfak k…ôm in.  
\v 26 M…ôto Pita t…ôm…®tol-ip…ôr m…®n m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆ètul, io et…ômim …ôm tahmen lam.‚Äù\x - \xo 10:26 \xt W…ôk 14:13-15; Nol ∆èp…ôn 19:10 \x*  
\v 27 K…ôn Pita t…ômat…ôghat ilau Konilias k…ôn k…ômian im…ô. Pita t…ôplan m…ôm…ô net…ômim tep…ôt k…®notuwa r…ôk…®s kat…ôp…ôl…ôh.   
\p
\v 28 K…ôn Pita t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômat rafin n…ôkot…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô tasim e Lou r…ôha net…ôm Isrel m…ôm…ô okotuwa m…ôtan kiti…ôh ilat net…ôm s…ôn…ôm…ô net…ôm Isrel o kotuw…®n mot…ôtag ilat. M…ôto Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn k…ôm io e nap…®laiir…ôn m…ôm…ô es…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô suah kit in tamk…®m…®k e n…®gan…ômt…®n.  
\v 29 Tol-p…ôn n…ôhlan, nian n…ômotahl-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn ron io, em…ôs…ôn…ôn nat kit, n…®kik t…ômagien …ôm m…ôm…ô ekuwa. ?M…ôto iakolkeike m…ôm…ô ek…ôtap…ôh m…ôm…ô n…ômotahl-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn ron io m…ôm…ô ekuwa o naka?‚Äù   
\p
\v 30 K…ôn Konilias t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNian k…®s…®l t…®nuw…®n r…ôk…®s tahmen …ôh-roiu e tri k…®lok ehnaip…ôn, emat…ôfak …ôp…ôh e r…ôhak nim…ô. K…ôn roiu ag…®n suah kit it…ôm r…ôhan nat…®mnat t…ôhag-…ôhag t…ôtul aup…ôn-in io,  
\v 31 k…ôn m…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòKonilias. Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôto r…ôk…®s r…ôham n…ôfak…ôn, k…ôn m…ôsaluin…ôn nat w…®r m…®n it…ôm ik natol k…ôm ian-rat m…®n.  
\v 32 Ahl-ip…ôn net…ômim neen kotuw…®n …ôp…ôh Jopa o suah kit …ôh-ik…®n, n…ôrg…®n u Saimon Pita m…ôm…ô otuwa. In t…ôtat…®g e nim…ô r…ôha suah kit, n…ôrg…®n u Saimon, u it…ôm tatol nat…®mnat m…®n e nuwig…® kau. R…ôhan nim…ô tat…ôtul iu…ôhk…®r o it…ôh…ôi.‚Äô  
\v 33 K…ôn ekahl-ip…®n…ô u…ôhai …ôm n…ôghat…ôn ron ik. K…ôn t…ôw…®r p…®k m…ôm…ô ik n…ômuwa. It…®mat rafin u ik…®n-u e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n ioat…ôt…ôl…®g-in ik m…ôm…ô onak…ôn-ipa rafin nat…®mnat it…ôm I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ômos-ip…®n…ô m…ôm…ô onak…ôn-ipa k…ôm it…®mat.‚Äù   
\s1 Pita t…ôm…ôghat  
\p
\v 34 K…ôn Pita t…ôm…ôghat m…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúRoiu en…®tun m…ôm…ô s…ôn…ôm…ô noanol r…ôha Isrel …ôm it…ôm Uhg…®n n…®kin tagien olat,\x - \xo 10:34 \xt Dut 10:17; Rom 2:11 \x*  
\v 35 m…ôto n…®kin tagien o net…ômim ik…®n m…®n rafin it…ôm koat…®siai-in ne moatol nat it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p.   
\p
\v 36 ‚ÄúIt…ômat n…ôkot…®tun r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ôm Isrel it…ôm tat…ôn namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn ilat Uhg…®n e Iesu Kristo it…ôm in I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôha net…ôm rafin.  
\v 37 It…ômat n…ôkot…®tun nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm Iesu et…ôm Nasaret t…ômol …ôp…ôh ik…®n m…®n e Jutia t…ôm…ôtuoun e Kalili. In t…ômol nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh uaris…®g e w…ôk r…ôha Jon Baptais it…ôm tat…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm net…ômim m…ôm…ô ok…ôike kol baptais elat.\x - \xo 10:37 \xt Mat 4:12-17 \x*  
\v 38 Iesu …ôh, Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun mos-ip…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n ne n…ôsan…ôn…ôn k…ôm in, k…ôn m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g ilau min, in t…ômuw…®n e ik…®n m…®n matol nat w…®r m…®n, k…ôn matol-w…®r net…ômim it…ôm Setan t…ôm…ôlis ilat.   
\p
\v 39 ‚ÄúIt…®mat emot…ôplan nat…®mnat it…ôm in t…ômol …ôp…ôh Jerusalem ne ik…®n m…®n …ôp…ôh Jutia. K…ôn it…®mat emot…ôplan nian net…ômim k…ômotoh k…ôt…ôtu-p…ôr e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau k…ôn t…®m…®s.  
\v 40 M…ôto Uhg…®n t…ômol t…ômeg…ôh m…®n e nian it…ôm tatol k…®s…®l lan, k…ôn matol …ôp in k…ôm net…ômim neen m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan m…ôm…ô in t…ôm…ômeg…ôh m…®n.  
\v 41 S…ôn…ôm…ô net…ômim rafin k…ômot…ôplan in, m…ôto net…ôm …ôm un it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun ilat m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan, it…®mat …ôh in…ôh emotagw…ôn kiti…ôh it…®mat min nian t…ôm…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn.\x - \xo 10:41 \xt Luk 24:42-43; W…ôk 1:8 \x*   
\p
\v 42 ‚ÄúK…ôn in t…ôm…ôn-ipa k…ôm it…®mat m…ôm…ô ekot…ôn Iesu k…ôm net…ômim, k…ôn mot…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ôm…®l…ôs-ip…ôr r…ôk…®s in m…ôm…ô in otakil nol…ôn r…ôha net…ômim rafin it…ôm koat…ômeg…ôh ne it…ôm k…®not…®m…®s r…ôk…®s.\x - \xo 10:42 \xt W…ôk 17:31; 1 Pita 4:5 \x*  
\v 43 Ien m…®n rafin r…ôha Uhg…®n aup…ôn k…ômoat…ôn-iar…ôp in m…ôm…ô, net…ômim rafin it…ôm koat…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn lan, Uhg…®n otaf…ôl r…ôk…®s r…ôhalat m…®n nol…ôn rat m…®n e n…ôrg…® in Iesu.‚Äù\x - \xo 10:43 \xt Aes 53:5-6; W…ôk 2:38 \x*   
\s1 Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômuwa o Iaihlu…ô m…®n, net…ôm u s…ôn…ôm…ô net…ôm Isrel  
\p
