\v 3 Nian t…ôm…ôtamnu Jemes, m…ôplan m…ôm…ô net…ôm Isrel n…®kilat t…ômagien p…®k ron. K…ôn in t…ômat…®g mask…ôl…®m m…®n Pita. T…ômatol nat u e nian k…ômatol lafet mil lan R…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn ne Pret U Is T…®k…ô Lan.  
\v 4 Nian t…®nask…ôl…®m r…ôk…®s Pita, k…ôn t…ôm…®l…ôs-ip…ôn e kalapus. K…ôn Herot t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô mopael sikistin okoat…ôtlos…®g-in, kuw…®t kuw…®t e aua m…®n rafin e n…ôraui…ôg…ôn ne lap…®n. K…ôn Herot tolkeike m…ôm…ô otiuw-iar…ôp t…ôtul e n…®gan…ômt…® net…ômim nian lafet t…®nol namnun.  
\v 5 M…ôto nian Pita t…ôm…ôtat…®g e kalapus, k…ôn net…ôm r…ôha nim…ôfak k…ômot…ôfak-p…ôn …ôskas…®k ron k…ôm Uhg…®n.   
\s1 Uhg…®n t…ôm…®l…ôs-iar…ôp Pita e kalapus  
\p
\v 6 E lap…®n it…ôm olaw…®g in, k…ôn Herot tiuw-iar…ôp, Pita t…ôm…ôtap…®l ilug…®n e mopael k…ôiu, k…ôm…ôlis nelm…®n mil e sen k…ôiu, k…ôtu-p…ôn kit e mopael kit, k…ôn k…ôtu-p…ôn kit e mopael kit m…®n. K…ôn mopael k…ôiu katu…ôtul matuehm nafilu…ô e kalapus.\fig |alt="Peter with sleeping guards and soldiers" src="LB00336B.TIF" size="col" loc="Act 12:6" ref="W…ôk 12:6" \fig*  
\v 7 Roiu ag…®n-…ôh, nagelo kit r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô tiet-pa, k…ôn t…ômasi…ô m…ôhag-…ôhag e n…®p…ôgnoa kalapus. T…ômekek n…®kal…® Pita k…ôn m…ôhgaiir lan. K…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!∆ètul u…ôhai!‚Äù K…ôn sen mil k…ômu…®sas at…®p e nelm…® Pita mil.   
\p
\v 8 K…ôn nagelo t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUw…®n e r…ôham put ne nat…®mnat.‚Äù K…ôn Pita tuw…®n elat. K…ôn t…ôn-ip…ôn m…®n k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUw…®nin r…ôham kot, k…ôn m…ôt…ôu-pa io.‚Äù  
\v 9 K…ôn Pita t…ôm…ôt…ôu-p…ôn miaiet e n…®p…ôgnoa kalapus, m…ôto in t…ôs…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô nat…®mnat m…®n u nagelo tatol lan in n…®pahrien…ôn. N…®kin t…ôht m…ôm…ô tatehm nat kit tahmen e nap…®laiir…ôn.  
\v 10 K…ômualiw…ôk muapr…ôk…®s-in mopael kit it…ôm tatehm kalapus, k…ôn mualiw…ôk muapr…ôk…®s-in m…®n mopael kit m…®n, k…ôn k…ômuea e namnu toa it…ôm k…ômil…ôk…®n e iaen. Toa u tatuag-p…ôn e taon asol. Nian k…ômuea iu…ôhk…®r ron k…ôn t…ômer…ôh at…®p k…ôn k…ômiaiet-p…ôn ik…®n. Nian k…ômualiw…ôk m…ôs…®n mian e suat…®p, k…ôn …ômun nagelo t…ôm…®k…ô m…®n.\x - \xo 12:10 \xt W…ôk 5:19 \x*   
\p
\v 11 K…ôn Pita in t…®n…®tun m…ôm…ô s…ôn…ôm…ô nap…®laiir…ôn, k…ôn t…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúRoiu en…®tun …ôtuat…®p m…ôm…ô I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ômahl-ipa r…ôhan nagelo t…ômuwa m…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s io e nat naka it…ôm Herot tolkeike m…ôm…ô otol lak it…ôm net…ôm Isrel k…ômoatolkeike m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan.‚Äù   
\p
\v 12 Nian Pita t…®n…®tun m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ôm…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s in, k…ôn t…ômuw…®n …ôp…ôh e nim…ô r…ôha Meri, mama r…ôha Jon Mak. Net…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n tep…ôt k…ômotuwa kiti…ôh moat…ôfak-p…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô otasitu lan.  
\v 13 K…ôn Pita t…ôm…ôht-…ôht toa e iat r…ôha nim…ô …ôh, k…ôn p…ôtan iolw…ôk kit, n…ôrg…®n u Rota, t…ômaiu muw…®n m…ôm…ô karm…ô pah …ôh tat…ôht-…ôht toa.  
\v 14 Nian t…ôm…ôto n…ôwia Pita, k…ôn t…ôm…®tun m…ôm…ô in Pita pahrien. K…ôn n…®kin t…ômagien p…®k ag…®n-…ôh k…ôn taluin ner…ôh…ôn e toa m…ôto t…ômaiu m…®t…ôl…®g muw…®n m…ôplan net…ômim u koat…ôfak, k…ôn t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei, net…ômim, Pita …ôp…ôh ihlu…ô e toa tat…ôtul!‚Äù   
\p
\v 15 M…ôto kot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúAh. Ik ialm…ôl.‚Äù M…ôto in t…ômat…ôk…ôike mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!K…ôp! Iat…ôn pahrien.‚Äù K…ôn ilat kot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô naka r…ôhan nagelo ti…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 16 M…ôto Pita tat…ôk…ôike mat…ôht-…ôht toa. K…ôn k…ômotuw…®n ker…ôh e toa, k…ôn nian k…ômot…ôplan in, n…®kilat t…ômaut p…®k ron.  
\v 17 M…ôto Pita t…ôm…®l…ôs-ip…ôr nelm…®n mef…ôtutu ilat m…ôm…ô ok…ôsot…ôghat…ôn. K…ôn mat…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô t…ômahro nulan I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôm…®l…ôs-iar…ôp in e kalapus. K…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOt…ôn-ip…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u k…ôm Jemes ne piatat m…®n e nim…ôfak.‚Äù K…ôn t…ômiet mag…®m matuw…®n ik p…®s…®n kit m…®n.   
\p
\v 18 K…ôm…ôn law…®gin, mopael m…®n it…ôm k…ômoatehm Pita e kalapus, k…ômot…ôtap…ôh-…ôtap…ôh olat m…®n, k…ôn m…®not…ôruru …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôm…ô Pita t…ômahruw…®n.\x - \xo 12:18 \xt W…ôk 5:22-24 \x*  
\v 19 K…ôn nian Herot t…ôm…ôto m…ôm…ô Pita t…ôm…®k…ô, k…ôn t…ômahl-ip…ôn mopael m…®n m…ôm…ô okoteg…ôs-in. M…ôto nian mopael m…®n k…ôm…ôsot…ôplan…ôn, k…ôn Herot t…ômaun-in mopael m…®n it…ôm k…ômotehm kalapus m…ôtap…ôh olat m…ôm…ô Pita t…ômahrol mag…®m. M…ôto ilat kot…ôruru k…ôn in t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…®k mopael m…®n …ôh kan kohamnu ilat. K…ôn Herot t…ômiet Jutia muw…®n e taon kit Sisaria mat…®g ik…®n o nian neen.   
\s1 Kig Herot Akripa Kiti…ôh t…ôm…®m…®s  
\p
\v 20 E nian …ôh, Kig Herot Akripa Kiti…ôh nem…ôha t…ômol p…®k t…ômet…ôhau net…ôm kotat…®g e taon mil …ôh, Taea ne Saeton. K…ôn net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha taon mil …ôh k…ômotuwa kiti…ôh k…ôn motuw…®n m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan kig m…ôm…ô okotaru nego, m…ôto-inu net…ôm im…ôlat ik…®n kotuw…®n katos-n…ômt…®n nagw…ôn…ôn im…ô kig ik…®n. M…ôto aup…ôn ilat k…ômotuw…®n mot…ôplan kig, k…ômot…ôghat ilat suah kit n…ôrg…®n u Plastus, it…ôm tatehm w…®r nat…®mnat e nim…ô r…ôha Kig Herot, motiuw-p…ôn m…ôm…ô ot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn ilat.   
\p
\v 21 E nian it…ôm Kig Herot t…ôm…®t…ôpun lan m…ôm…ô otuw…®n m…ôplan ilat, k…ôn t…ômuw…®n e r…ôhan nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n it…ôm tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô in tat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. K…ôn t…ômuwa m…ôp…ôl…ôh e ik…®n im…ô kig, k…ôn mat…ôghat k…ôm net…ômim.  
