\v 1 K…ôn Pol t…ômaliw…ôk m…®n muw…®n …ôp…ôh Tepe ne Listra. K…ôn ik…®n …ôh, et…ômim kit …ôh-ik…®n r…ôha Iesu, n…ôrg…®n u Timoti. Mama r…ôhan in noanol kit r…ôha Isrel, m…ôto r…ôhan tata in et…ôm Kris.\x - \xo 16:1 \xt W…ôk 14:6; 2 Tim 1:5 \x*  
