\p
\v 13 K…ôn e Sapat, nian r…ôha n…ôfak…ôn, emotiet e taon …ôh k…ôn motuw…®n …ôp…ôh l…ôhau e n…ôhau kit it…ôm emot…ôto m…ôm…ô net…ômim kotuw…®n ik…®n kat…ôfak. K…ôn emotuw…®n moat…ôp…ôl…ôh kat…ôghat it…®mat n…®p…®tan it…ôm k…ômotaup…ôn motuwa kat…ôp…ôl…ôh.  
\v 14 K…ôn p…ôtan Tuatira kit …ôh-ik…®n tat…ôt…ôl…®g-in it…®mat, n…ôrg…®n u Litia. In p…ôtan it…ôm tatol-sal…®m-in n…®m…ôhan n…ôgu…®-naris u nian rafin n…®m…ôhan …ôh n…ômt…®n ti…ôk…®s p…®k. P…ôtan …ôh nian rafin in tat…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n, k…ôn I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ômol n…®kin t…®m…ôtm…ôt…®g m…ôm…ô ot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm Pol tat…ôn.  
