\p
\v 16 K…ôn nian kit, nian emoatuw…®n ik…®n r…ôha n…ôfak…ôn …ôh, k…ôn p…ôtan …ôk…ôku kit t…ôm…ôplan it…®mat e suat…®p. In slef r…ôha net…ômim neen it…ôm k…ômotos-n…ômt…®n. P…ôtan …ôh narm…®n rat kit t…ôtat…®g lan it…ôm tol in tat…ôn-iar…ôp nat…®mnat it…ôm ot…ôpanuwa. K…ôn matol win e m…ôni tep…ôt r…ôha r…ôhan net…ôm-iasol m…®n m…ôto-inu net…ômim kot…ôtou ilat m…ôm…ô ilat okot…ôto r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn.  
\v 17 K…ôn in t…ômatuaris…®g-in it…®mat Pol, k…ôn mat…ôn …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNet…ôm u, net…ôm r…ôha Uhg…®n u in il…®s, il…®s p…®k. Koat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat suat…®p r…ôha Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô in otosmeg…ôh net…ômim lan.‚Äù\x - \xo 16:17 \xt Mak 1:24 \x*   
\p
