\v 32 K…ôn k…ômu…ôn-ip…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô k…ôm in ne net…ômim it…ôm kotat…®g ilat min.  
\v 33 Nat …ôpnap…®n lap…®n ag…®n, m…ôto suah …ôh t…ômit ilau muw…®n maikuas e n…®m…ôg…ôm m…®n e n…®p…ôt…®lau it…ôm k…ômalis ilau ik…®n. K…ôn e nian …ôm …ôh, k…ômol baptais lan ilat r…ôhan m…®n.  
\v 34 K…ôn in t…ômit Pol ne Saelas muw…®n …ôp…ôh iman ik…®n mos-ip…ôn nagw…ôn…ôn k…ôm ilau. K…ôn in ne r…ôhan m…®n rafin n…®kilat t…ômagien m…ôrioah m…ôto-inu k…ômot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e Uhg…®n.   
\p
\v 35 Nian t…ômian, et…ôm r…ôha kot mil …ôh ku…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm mopael m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOkotuw…®n ker…ôh e suah mil …ôh katian.‚Äù   
\p
\v 36 K…ôn suah …ôh et…ôm r…ôha kalapus t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Pol m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm r…ôha kot mil k…ômu…ôn m…ôm…ô ekoter…ôh et…ôlau nakatian, k…ôn iaiet m…ôtian k…ôn mu…ôtul m…ôt…®g.‚Äù   
\p
\v 37 M…ôto Pol t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm mopael m…®n …ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Ei, m…ôto naka …ôh? It…®mlau et…ôm Rom mil.\f + \fr 16:37 \ft Ok…ôm…ô suah kit in et…ôm Rom, m…ôto kat…ôtu-p…ôn n…ôghat…ôn kit lan, k…ôn lou kit …ôh-ik…®n r…ôhalat m…ôm…ô aup…ôn kapman otol nalp…®n…ôn k…ôm in, m…ôto in ot…ôk…ôike m…ôtul e kot m…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôwtain n…ôghat…ôn kat…ôtu-p…ôn lan. Afin e W…ôk 25:15-16.\f* K…ôn et…ôm r…ôha kot mil …ôh k…ôsu…ôplan…ôn nat kit m…ôm…ô emioal t…ôrat, m…ôto e n…®gan…ômt…® net…ômim k…ômotalis it…®mlau, k…ôn k…®l…ôs-ip…ôn it…®mlau e kalapus. ?K…ôn roiu kioalkeike m…ôm…ô oekiaiet anion …ôm? !K…ôp! Ilau …ôm oku…ôike muea ik…®n-u k…ôn mial…ôs-iar…ôp it…®mlau.‚Äù   
\p
\v 38 K…ôn mopael m…®n …ôh k…ômotuw…®n k…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm et…ôm r…ôha kot mil …ôh. K…ôn nian k…ômu…ôto m…ôm…ô Pol ne Saelas ilau et…ôm Rom mil, ilau k…ômu…ôg…®n p…®k.  
\v 39 K…ôn k…ômian mu…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Pol ne Saelas m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei, k…ôsi! Emioal t…ôrat et…ômlau.‚Äù K…ôn uaris…®g kiaiet ilau motiet e n…®p…ôg noa kalapus, k…ôn mu…ôn-ip…ôn w…®r k…ôm ilau m…ôm…ô okiaiet e taon …ôh.   
\p
\v 40 K…ôn Pol ne Saelas, ilau k…ômiaiet e kalapus mian e nim…ô r…ôha Litia. Ik…®n …ôh k…ômu…ôplan piatat ne w…®n…®tat m…®n r…ôha nim…ôfak, k…ôn mu…ôghat m…ôs…®n k…ôm ilat m…ôtial…ôs-ip…ôr n…®kilat. K…ôn uaris…®g u, kiaiet m…ôtian.   
\c 17  
\s1 Pol ne Saelas k…ômian …ôp…ôh Tesalonaeka  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn Pol ne Saelas k…ômualiw…ôk mian-p…ôn …ôp…ôh e taon mil …ôh Amfipolis ne Apolonia, mueia miaet-pa e taon …ôh Tesalonaeka. Ik…®n …ôh, nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn kit …ôh-ik…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel.  
\v 2 K…ôn Pol t…ômol tahmen …ôm e it…ôm tatol nian m…®n, t…ômuw…®n …ôp…ôh im…ô e nim…ô …ôh. K…ôn e Sapat k…®s…®l ilat net…ôm …ôh noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…ômoatol n…ôghat…ôn tep…ôt o Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 3 In tat…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNaoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn w…®r ag…®n-…ôh m…ôm…ô Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa, ot…ôpan…ôto nahm…ô…ôn e n…®p…ôt…®n, muwa m…ôtoarus m…®m…®s, k…ôn Uhg…®n ot…ôpanosmeg…ôh m…®n in e n…®m…®s…ôn. Iesu u it…ôm iat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat, inu Kristo …ôh.‚Äù  
\v 4 Ilat neen k…ômot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, k…ôn k…ômot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn Pol ne Saelas. K…ôn net…ôm Kris tep…ôt it…ôm koat…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n, ne n…®p…®tan asol tep…ôt it…ôm koat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e n…®p…®tan m…®n, k…ômot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn ilau.   
\p
\v 5 M…ôto net…ôm-iasol r…ôha noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel, k…ômotet…ôhak, k…ôn motuw…®n moateg…ôs-in net…ôm nol t…ôfag…ô, …ôp…ôh e n…®kal suat…®p m…®n ne ik…®n m…®n, motuwa m…®noatos ilat m…®n, k…ôn m…®noatol n…ôrat…ôn tep…ôt …ôp…ôh e taon …ôh. K…ôn k…ômotuw…®n e nim…ô r…ôha suah kit n…ôrg…®n u Jeson, moteat…ôp nafilu…ô e nim…ô, moateg…ôs-in Pol ne Saelas. K…ômotolkeike m…ôm…ô okot…®l…ôs-ip…ôn ilau e nelm…® kaonsel …ôh-ik…®n …ôh.   
\p
\v 6 Nian k…ôm…ôsot…ôplan…ôn ilau, k…ôn k…ômotask…ôl…®m Jeson ne piatat m…®n neen mot…ômki-p…ôn ilat m…ôm…ô okot…ôtul aup…ôn in net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha kaonsel. K…ôn k…ômotag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh moat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSuah mil …ôh Pol ne Saelas k…ôtioal nat t…ôrat tep…ôt e ik…®n m…®n, k…ôn m…®nuea e taon r…ôhatat.  
\v 7 K…ôn suah u Jeson t…ômaun-in ilau kian iman ik…®n, m…ôto ilat koat…ôtg…ôhl lou r…ôha Sisa it…ôm tat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e n…®t…ôn m…®n. Ilat koat…ôn m…ôm…ô I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô kit m…®n …ôh-ik…®n t…ôtat…®g, n…ôrg…®n u Iesu.‚Äù\x - \xo 17:7 \xt Luk 23:2; Jon 19:12 \x*  
\v 8 Nian noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…ômot…ôn n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, motol net…ômim ne net…ôm-iasol m…®n …ôh k…®not…ôruru …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôm…ô okotol naka.  
\v 9 K…ôn net…ôm-iasol m…®n …ôh k…ômotol Jeson ne piatat m…®n k…ômotos-ip…ôn m…ôni neen, m…ôm…ô in n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn kit m…ôm…ô ok…ôsotol m…®n…ôn nat …ôh, k…ôn motahl-ip…ôn ilat koatuw…®n.   
\s1 Pol ne Saelas k…ômian …ôp…ôh Perea  
\p
\v 10 Nian t…®napin…ôp, k…ôn piatat m…®n ik…®n …ôh k…ômotahl-ip…ôn Pol ne Saelas m…ôm…ô okian e taon …ôh Perea. Nian k…ômiaiet-pa ik…®n …ôh, k…ômian e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel.  
\v 11 Noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel ik…®n …ôh n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat t…ôw…®r, mapr…ôk…®s-in net…ôm Tesalonaeka, m…ôto-inu kotolkeike p…®k m…ôm…ô okot…ôt…ôl…®g-in n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhalau. K…ôn nian rafin, koatafin w…®r e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, moateg…ôs-in m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhalau t…ôtuat…®p o k…ôp.  
\v 12 M…ôto-inu e nol…ôn …ôh, k…ôn tep…ôt k…ômot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e Iesu. K…ôn n…®p…®tan asol m…®n Kris tep…ôt, ne net…ôm Kris tep…ôt k…ômot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e Iesu.   
\p
\v 13 M…ôto nian noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel …ôp…ôh Tesalonaeka k…ômot…ôto m…ôm…ô Pol tat…ôn-iar…ôp m…®n n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n …ôp…ôh Perea, k…ôn ilat k…ômotuwa m…®n …ôp…ôh ik…®n m…®noatol net…ôm Perea k…®notol m…®n t…ôm…ôht k…ôm ilau.  
\v 14 K…ôn e nian …ôm …ôh, piatat m…®n k…ômotahl-ip…ôn m…®n Pol tuw…®n …ôp…ôh it…ôh…ôi muw…®n e nego muw…®n Atens, map…ôs …ôm Saelas ne Timoti k…ôtuat…®g …ôp…ôh Perea.  
\v 15 K…ôn net…ômim it…ôm k…ômotit Pol moatuw…®n Atens, k…®noat…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n Perea, Pol tahl…ôpis ilat m…ôm…ô okot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Saelas ne Timoti m…ôm…ô okuaut u…ôhai …ôm mian mu…ôplan m…®n in.   
\s1 Pol …ôp…ôh Atens  
\p
\v 16 Nian Pol t…ômat…ôsahgin Saelas ne Timoti …ôp…ôh Atens, in t…ôm…ôto t…ôrat p…®k m…ôto-inu nian taliw…ôk m…ôtan ik…®n …ôh, m…ôplan ik…®n …ôh t…ôrioah e narm…® nat m…®n.  
\v 17 M…ôto-inu o nat …ôh, k…ôn in tuw…®n …ôp…ôh e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel ilat net…ôm Isrel ne Iaihlu…ô m…®n it…ôm koat…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n, moat…ôghat p…®k o nat …ôh. K…ôn nian rafin in tatuw…®n ik…®n katol maket ik…®n mat…ôghat k…ôm net…ôm …ôpnap…®n m…®n …ôm.\x - \xo 17:17 \xt W…ôk 18:19 \x*  
\v 18 K…ôn i…ôg…ôtun m…®n neen net…ôm Kris, k…ôtaun-in ilat Epikiurien ne S…®toik,\f + \fr 17:18 \ft Epikiurien ne S…®toik - I…ôg…ôtun m…®n neen it…ôm koateg…ôs-in n…®pahrien…ôn. Ilat Epikiurien koat…ôn m…ôm…ô nat…®mnat it…ôm tatol suah kit n…®kin tagien, inu n…ôuk…ôt…®n r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn t…ôw…®r. Ilat S…®toik koat…ôn m…ôm…ô t…ôw…®r ok…ôm…ô suah kit t…ôs…ôto…ôn nagien…ôn ne nahm…ô…ôn e n…®kin.\f* ilat m…®n koat…ôghat. Ilat neen koat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Suah …ôh t…ôm…®l…ôs …ôm n…ôghat…ôn …ôp…ôh kit e suat…®p mat…ôn, kahrm…ô tat…ôn naka …ôp…ôh?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn net…ômim neen kot…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…®mat ekot…ôto m…ôm…ô tat…ôghat-in uhg…®n m…®n r…ôha ik…®n p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n.‚Äù Koat…ôghat n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu Pol tat…ôghat-in Iesu, mat…ôn m…ôm…ô t…ôm…®m…®s m…ôto Uhg…®n t…ômosmeg…ôh m…®n.   
\p
\v 19 K…ôn k…ômotaun-in-p…ôn Pol m…ôm…ô otuwa m…ôtul e n…®gan…ômt…® kaonsel r…ôha net…ôm koat…ôp…ôl…ôh e n…®tot …ôh Areopakus. K…ôn kaonsel …ôh t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEkotolkeike m…ôm…ô ekot…®tun n…®p…ôt…® n…ôghat…ôn wi it…ôm nakat…ôn.\fig |alt="Mars‚Äô Hill and Areopagus" src="HK00355B.TIF" size="col" loc="Act 17:19-28" ref="W…ôk 17:19" \fig*  
\v 20 N…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôh neen, ekot…ôto m…ôm…ô tol p…®s…®n ag…®n-…ôh, k…ôn ekotolkeike m…ôm…ô ekot…®tun n…®p…ôt…®n.‚Äù  
\v 21 K…ômot…ôghat n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu net…ôm Atens ne net…ôm ik p…®s…®n m…®n it…ôm k…ômotuwa Atens, kotolkeike m…ôm…ô okot…ôp…ôl…ôh …ôm kat…ôt…ôl…®g-in n…ôghat…ôn wi m…®n …ôh, k…ôn mot…ôuhlin w…®r n…ôn…ôn lan.   
\p
\v 22 K…ôn Pol t…ôtul e n…®gan…ômt…® net…ôm r…ôha kaonsel …ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNet…ôm Atens. Io en…ôplan r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô r…ôhat…ômat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn tep…ôt tatuw…®n o uhg…®n m…®n.  
\v 23 Nian io etaliw…ôk ik…®n-u imat…ômat ik…®n, mat…ôplan ik…®n n…ôkoat…ôfak m…®n ik…®n ne narm…® nat m…®n, k…ôn em…ôplan n…ôghat…ôn kit it…ôm it…ômat n…ômot…ôte-p…ôn r…ôk…®s e k…ôpiel kit m…ôm…ô, \sc Inu ik…®n kat…ôfak-p…ôn k…ôm uhg…®n kit it…ôm it…®mat ekot…ôruru\sc*. M…ôto uhg…®n it…ôm it…ômat n…ôkoat…ôfak k…ôm in, it…ôm n…ôkot…ôruru, Uhg…®n …ôh in…ôh it…ôm io iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat.  
\v 24 Uhg…®n …ôh in…ôh t…ômol n…ôpt…ôn u, ne nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm koatat…®g lan, k…ôn in mat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e neai ne n…ôpt…ôn, in t…ôsat…®g…ôn e nim…ôfak m…®n it…ôm kitat …ôm net…ômim k…ômotol.  
\v 25 Nat kit t…ôs…®k…ô…ôn ron it…ôm kitat net…ômim kot…®tun nol…ôn kos-ip…ôn k…ôm in. M…ôto-inu in p…®s…®n …ôm tatos-ipa n…ômeg…ôh…ôn k…ôm kitat kiti…ôh kiti…ôh, matos-ipa nat…®mnat rafin k…ôm kitat.\x - \xo 17:25 \xt 1 King 8:27; W…ôk 7:48 \x*\x - \xo 17:25 \xt Sam 50:12 \x*  
\v 26 Aup…ôn, aup…ôn ag…®n-…ôh, in t…ômol …ôm suah kiti…ôh …ôm. K…ôn net…ôm rafin ik…®n m…®n k…ômotiet …ôm e suah …ôh, k…ôn in p…®s…®n …ôm t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu ilat rafin e ik…®n m…®n, k…ôn in p…®s…®n …ôm t…ôm…ôn nian it…ôm ilat okotan lan, ne nuant…ôn m…®n r…ôhalat.  
\v 27 Uhg…®n …ôh t…ômol n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô kitat rafin okot…ôk…ôike keg…ôs-in m…ôm…ô okotehm, tahmen e et…ômim it…ôm tateameam …ôpnap…®n …ôm m…ôm…ô otehm nat kit. M…ôto n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n …ôh, s…ôn…ôm…ô in is…ôu o kitat.\x - \xo 17:27 \xt Sam 145:18; Jer 23:23 \x*  
\v 28 Tahmen e it…ôm suah kit t…ôm…ôn aup…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòM…ôto-inu kitat koat…ôkul-p…ôn …ôm e Uhg…®n, k…ôn moatos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, moataliw…ôk, moatol nat…®mnat rafin.‚Äô K…ôn mahmen e suah kit r…ôhat…ômat it…ôm t…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s napu…ôn kit m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòKitat m…®n kitat nen…ôt…®n m…®n.‚Äô   
\p
\v 29 ‚ÄúM…ôto-inu kitat nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n, okol kitat k…ôsot…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô in tahmen e nat…®mnat it…ôm net…ômim koatol ilat e iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t, ne silfa ne k…ôpiel. In s…ôn…ôm…ô nat kit it…ôm suah kit t…®tun nol …ôm…ôn e nelm…®n o e r…ôhan nenat…®g…ôn. !K…ôp!\x - \xo 17:29 \xt Aes 40:18-20; 44:10-17; W…ôk 19:26 \x*   
\p
\v 30 ‚ÄúE nian …ôh aup…ôn it…ôm net…ômim kot…ôruru Uhg…®n, tahmen e it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômahtos…®g-in n…®gan…ômt…®n m…ôm…ô ot…ôs…ôplan…ôn nol…ôn rat m…®n …ôh. M…ôto roiu tat…ôn k…ôm kitat rafin e ik…®n m…®n rafin m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIt…ômat rafin on…ôkot…ôuhlin it…ômat e r…ôhat…ômat m…®n nol…ôn rat m…®n.‚Äô  
\v 31 In t…ôm…ôn n…ôhlan, meto inu in t…®n…ôm…®t…ôpun r…ôk…®s nian it…ôm in otakil nol…ôn lan r…ôha net…ômim, k…ôn in otol …ôm e suat…®p it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p. Uhg…®n t…®n…®t…ôpun r…ôk…®s et…ômim it…ôm otakil nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha net…ômim, k…ôn in t…®n…ômol r…ôk…®s k…ôm net…ômim m…ôm…ô in otol n…ôhlan, m…ôto-inu t…®nol r…ôk…®s suah …ôh t…ômeg…ôh e n…®m…®s…ôn.‚Äù\x - \xo 17:31 \xt Sam 96:13 \x*   
\p
\v 32 Nian ilat k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ômol suah kit t…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn, neen k…ômotalah-…ômnu, m…ôto neen kat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…®mat ekotolkeike m…ôm…ô ekot…ôto m…®n r…ôham n…ôghat…ôn.‚Äù  
\v 33 K…ôn Pol t…ômiet e n…ôghat…ôn …ôh r…ôha kaonsel.  
\v 34 K…ôn net…ômim neen kotuw…®n k…ôkul-p…ôn lan, moat…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e Iesu. Net…ôm …ôh kit n…ôrg…®n u Taionisi…ôs, in et…ôm kit r…ôha kaonsel …ôh, ne p…ôtan kit m…®n n…ôrg…®n u Tamaris, ne net…ômim neen m…®n.   
\c 18  
\s1 Pol t…ômuw…®n Korin  
\m
\v 1 Uaris…®g e nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh, Pol t…ômiet …ôh Atens, muw…®n e taon p…®s…®n kit m…®n, n…ôrg…®n u Korin.  
\v 2 Ik…®n …ôh, t…ôm…ôplan suah kit, in noanol r…ôha Isrel, n…ôrg…®n u Akwila. T…ômaiir …ôp…ôh Pontas, m…ôto t…ômuw…®n m…ôtat…®g …ôp…ôh Itali e taon asol …ôh Rom. Uaris…®g, k…ôn et…ôm Rom …ôh, Klotias it…ôm tat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e ik…®n m…®n, t…ômol lou kit m…ôm…ô noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel okot…ôk…ôike motiet Rom. K…ôn Akwila ne r…ôhan p…ôtan Prisila k…ômiaet mueia m…ôtuat…®g …ôp…ôh Korin. K…ôm…ôsuat…®g…ôn t…ôf…ôm…ôh k…ôn Pol tiet-pa, m…ôplan ilau.\x - \xo 18:2 \xt Rom 16:3 \x*  
\v 3 K…ôn m…ôtat…®g il…ôhal min ilau, mat…ôkul-p…ôn elau e w…ôk r…ôhalau, m…ôto-inu w…ôk r…ôhan r…ôha nos…ôn m…ôni tahmen …ôm …ôh w…ôk r…ôhalau. Ilat net…ôm r…ôha n…ôhl…ôn nim…ô tapol…ôn.\x - \xo 18:3 \xt W…ôk 20:34 \x*  
\v 4 K…ôn e nian rafin e Sapat, nian r…ôha n…ôfak…ôn, Pol ne noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel ne net…ôm Kris koatol n…ôghat…ôn tep…ôt …ôp…ôh e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, m…ôto-inu Pol tolkeike m…ôm…ô otiuw-pa ilat m…ôm…ô okot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e Iesu.   
\p
\v 5 K…ôn Saelas ne Timoti k…ômiaiet Masetonia, k…ôn nian k…ômiaiet-pa ik…®n …ôh, Pol t…ômap…ôs w…ôk k…ôn mat…ôn-iar…ôp …ôm nian rafin namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r mat…ôn w…®r k…ôm noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa.\x - \xo 18:5 \xt W…ôk 17:14-15 \x*  
\v 6 M…ôto ilat k…ômotet…ôhau, k…ôn moat…ôhai. K…ôn Pol t…ômorautin-orautin r…ôhan sot asol e n…®gan…ômt…®lat. K…ôn m…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô n…ôkotat…®g e n…ôrat…ôn lan nian Uhg…®n otakil net…ômim e Namnun Nian, m…ôto r…ôhat…ômat at…®p. T…ôtuoun …ôh-roiu, ekuw…®n m…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r o Iaihlu…ô m…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 18:6 \xt W…ôk 13:46,51; W…ôk 20:26 \x*  
\v 7 K…ôn in t…ômiet elat muw…®n m…ôtat…®g e nim…ô r…ôha suah kit s…ôn…ôm…ô noanol r…ôha Isrel, m…ôto in tat…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n, n…ôrg…®n u Titias Jastas. R…ôhan nim…ô in e n…®kal nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel.  
\v 8 K…ôn Krispas u in tat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e nim…ô …ôh, in ne r…ôhan m…®n, ilat k…ômotahat…ôt…ô e I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. K…ôn net…ôm Korin tep…ôt m…®n k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Pol, k…ôn k…ômotahat…ôt…ô e Iesu, k…ôn kol baptais elat.   
\p
\v 9 K…ôn nian kit lap…®n, Pol t…ôm…ôplan nat kit tahmen e nap…®laiir…ôn. E nap…®laiir…ôn …ôh, I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôm…ôghat k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆ès…ôgin…ôn ilat. Uw…®n m…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn m…ôsameg…ôn,  
\v 10 m…ôto-inu kilau min ik. Net…ômim okol k…ôsot…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn ik, m…ôto-inu net…ômim tep…ôt e taon …ôh ilat r…ôhak net…ômim m…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 18:10 \xt Jos 1:9; Aes 41:10 \x*  
\v 11 K…ôn Pol t…ômat…®g ik…®n …ôh nup kiti…ôh k…ôn m…ôw…®g sikis, mat…ôg…ôtun net…ômim e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.   
\s1 Net…ôm Isrel k…ômot…®l…ôs-ip…ôn  //  Pol e kot  
\p
\v 12 K…ôn nian Kalio, in kapman r…ôha net…ôm Akaea, k…ôn net…ôm Isrel k…ômotuwa kiti…ôh motask…ôl…®m Pol mot…®l…ôs motuw…®n e kot.  
\v 13 K…ôn mot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSuah u t…ôtalkut m…ôm…ô otiuw-p…ôn net…ômim m…ôm…ô okot…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n e nol…ôn kit it…ôm t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn e Lou.‚Äù   
\p
\v 14 K…ôn Pol t…ôm…ôtul m…ôm…ô ot…ôghat, m…ôto Kalio t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNet…ôm Isrel. Ot…ôt…ôl…®g-in-tu. Ok…ôm…ô nat u in nat kit t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn, o t…ôs…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn lou, it…ômat n…ôkot…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô ek…ôike m…ôto n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhat…ômat.  
\v 15 M…ôto, n…ôghat…ôn u in musmus …ôm kit r…ôhat…ômat e n…ôr…®g m…®n ne nat…®mnat m…®n r…ôha Lou r…ôhat…ômat, k…ôn t…ôtat…®g …ôm et…ômat m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôn k…ôl…ôh…ôu w…®r. Io n…®kik t…ôsagien…ôn m…ôm…ô ekakil nat tol n…ôhlan kit.‚Äù  
\v 16 K…ôn in mahl-iar…ôp ilat e kot.  
\v 17 K…ôn nian k…ômotuw…®n ihlu…ô, …ômun k…ômotask…ôl…®m Sostenes u et…ôm-iasol r…ôha nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. K…ôn k…ômotoh k…ômotoh …ôp…ôh e nafilu…ô e nim…ô kot. M…ôto Kalio t…ôsol…ôn nat kit m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-i…ôhau ilat.   
\s1 Pol t…ôm…®t…ôl…®g Antiok …ôp…ôh Siria  
\p
\v 18 Pol t…ômat…®g nian tep…ôt …ôp…ôh Korin ilat piatat m…®n. K…ôn uaris…®g tap…ôs ilat muw…®n ik…®n …ôh-ik…®n Kegkria. Aup…ôn Pol t…ômol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn kit k…ôm Uhg…®n, k…ôn ik…®n-u in t…ôm…ôte m…®n …ôm noanun matol namnun n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn lan r…ôhan. K…ôn in t…ômos m…®n nego kit ik…®n …ôh m…®t…ôl…®g-pa Siria. K…ôn Akwila ne Prisila k…ômu…ôt…ôu-p…ôn in.\x - \xo 18:18 \xt Nam 6:18; W…ôk 21:24 \x*  
\v 19-21 Nian k…ômotuwa e taon …ôh Efesas, il…ôhal k…ôm…ôhaluar. K…ôn Pol t…ômuw…®n …ôp…ôh im…ô e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, k…ôn k…ômot…ôn n…ôghat…ôn tep…ôt. Ilat k…ômot…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô otat…®g m…ôs…®n ilat min ilat. M…ôto in t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEi k…ôsi, k…ôp…ô. Okol esat…®g…ôn.‚Äù M…ôto nian in t…ômiet t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô Uhg…®n tolkeike m…ôm…ô ekuwa m…®n, k…ôn epanuwa m…®n m…ôplan it…ômat.‚Äù K…ôn in t…ômos nego kit miet Efesas, m…ôto t…ômap…ôs Akwila ne Prisila k…ôtuat…®g ik…®n …ôh.   
\p
\v 22 Nian Pol t…ômuwa e taon …ôh Sisaria, k…ôn muar. K…ôn maliw…ôk muw…®n m…ôm…ô ot…ôplan net…ôm r…ôha nim…ôfak …ôp…ôh Jerusalem. K…ôn uaris…®g, t…ôm…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n …ôp…ôh Antiok.  
\v 23 T…ômat…®g m…ôs…®n ik…®n …ôh, k…ôn miet m…®n maliw…ôk muw…®n-p…ôn …ôp…ôh Kalesia ne Fritia ik…®n matem …ôskas…®k net…ôm r…ôha Iesu.   
\s1 Apolos t…ômuw…®n Efesas ne Korin  
\p
\v 24 K…ôn suah kit t…ômuwa …ôp…ôh Efesas, in noanol kit r…ôha Isrel, n…ôrg…®n u Apolos. In t…ômaiir …ôp…ôh Aleksantria, k…ôn in et…ôm w…®r kit r…ôha n…ôghat…ôn, k…ôn m…®tun w…®r m…®n n…ôghat…ôn m…®n e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 25 Ilat k…ômoat…ôg…ôtun r…ôk…®s in e suat…®p r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. K…ôn nian rafin n…®g…ôm tatu…ôp e n…®kin o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhan e Iesu in t…ôtuat…®p t…ôtuat…®p. M…ôto in t…®tun …ôm nol…ôn baptais it…ôm Jon t…ômatol aup…ôn.  
\v 26 K…ôn in t…ômat…ôn-iar…ôp …ôskas…®k n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n …ôp…ôh e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. Nian Prisila ne Akwila k…ômu…ôto in, k…ômiait m…ôhaluw…®n …ôp…ôh e r…ôhalau nim…ô, k…ôn mu…ôn-iar…ôp w…®r k…ôm in suat…®p r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 27 K…ôn nian Apolos tolkeike m…ôm…ô otuw…®n …ôp…ôh Akaea, k…ôn piatat m…®n …ôp…ôh Efesas k…ômotasitu lan mot…ôte naoa kit tuw…®n k…ôm net…ôm r…ôha Iesu …ôp…ôh Akaea, mot…ôtap…ôh olat m…ôm…ô kot…®tun nos…ôn Apolos motuw…®n …ôp…ôh im…ôlat ik…®n. K…ôn nian in t…ômuw…®n ik…®n …ôh, in t…ômasitu w…®r elat. Ilat m…®n …ôh, ilat k…ômotahat…ôt…ô e Iesu e n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 28 Apolos t…ômasitu elat n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu in et…ôm w…®r kit r…ôha n…ôghat…ôn, k…ôn in mat…ôn-iar…ôp w…®r e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa. K…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…® net…ômim, t…ômatoh-i…ôhau n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel.\x - \xo 18:28 \xt W…ôk 9:22 \x*   
\c 19  
\s1 Pol t…ômuw…®n m…®n Efesas  
\m
\v 1 Nian Apolos t…ôm…ôtat…®g …ôh …ôp…ôh Korin, Pol t…ôm…ôt…®p suat…®p kit …ôp…ôh il…®s ik…®n e n…®tot m…®n miet-pa …ôp…ôh Efesas. Ik…®n …ôh t…ôm…ôplan net…ômim neen r…ôha Iesu.\x - \xo 19:1 \xt 1 Kor 3:6 \x*  
\v 2 K…ôn t…ôm…ôtap…ôh olat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Tahro? ?Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…®nuwa m…ôrioah m…ôtat…®g et…ômat nian n…ômotahat…ôt…ô e Iesu, o k…ôp…ô?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…®mat esot…ôto ag…®n…ôn m…ôm…ô nat kit m…®n …ôh-ik…®n Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 19:2 \xt W…ôk 8:16 \x*   
\p
\v 3 K…ôn Pol t…ôm…ôtap…ôh olat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?M…ôto k…ômol baptais ahro nulan et…ômat?‚Äù  
\p K…ôn k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…ômol baptais et…®mat e nol…ôn baptais it…ôm Jon t…ômatol.‚Äù   
\p
\v 4 K…ôn Pol t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNol…ôn baptais it…ôm Jon t…ômatol tatol e net…ômim it…ôm koat…ôuhlin ilat e r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat m…®n. M…ôto Jon t…ômat…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…ôk…ôike motahat…ôt…ô e et…ômim it…ôm ot…ôpanuaris…®g in. Suah u in Iesu.‚Äù\x - \xo 19:4 \xt Mat 3:11 \x*  
\v 5 K…ôn nian net…ômim k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, k…ôn k…ômol baptais elat e n…ôrg…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu.  
\v 6 K…ôn nian Pol t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nelm…®n e r…ôhalat-kap…ô, Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômuwa m…ôrioah m…ôtat…®g elat. K…ôn k…®noat…ôghat e n…ôghat…ôn ik p…®s…®n m…®n, k…ôn moat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n tatos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat.\x - \xo 19:6 \xt W…ôk 8:17; W…ôk 10:44,46 \x*  
\v 7 K…ôn net…ôm …ôh, ilat rafin tuelef.   
\p
\v 8 K…ôn Pol t…ômatuw…®n e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel e m…ôw…®g k…®s…®l mat…ôn-iar…ôp …ôskas…®k n…ôghat…ôn e namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha Uhg…®n m…ôs…ôg…®n…ôn. K…ôn ilat min ilat, k…ômotol n…ôghat…ôn tep…ôt m…ôto-inu in tolkeike m…ôm…ô otiuw-pa ilat o n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 9 M…ôto net…ômim neen, r…ôhalat-kap…ô ti…ôk…®s p…®k m…ôm…ô okot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn. K…ôn k…ômoat…ôghat rat e suat…®p r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat e n…®gan…ômt…® net…ômim rafin. M…ôto-inu o nol…ôn m…®n …ôh, k…ôn Pol t…ômiet elat k…ôn mit net…ôm r…ôha Iesu kotuwa koatuaris…®g-in. K…ôn nian rafin ilat net…ômim koat…ôghat …ôp…ôh e nima s…®kul asol kit it…ôm suah kit, n…ôrg…®n u Tiranas, t…ômat…ôg…ôtun ik…®n aup…ôn.  
\v 10 K…ôn Pol t…ômatol w…ôk …ôh o nup k…ôiu api…ôpi…ô. M…ôto-inu t…ômatol n…ôhlan, k…ôn net…ômim it…ôm koatat…®g e ik…®n …ôh Esia, noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel ne net…ôm …ôpnap…®n …ôm, ilat rafin k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.   
\s1 Nen…ôt…® Skefa m…®n  
\p
\v 11 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômol Pol tatol nat p…®sp…®s m…®n it…ôm tol p…®s…®n ag…®n-…ôh.\x - \xo 19:11 \xt W…ôk 14:3 \x*  
\v 12 Nat…®mnat r…ôha Pol tahmen e iagk…ôsip ne nat…®mnat it…ôm t…ômatuw…®n lan, net…ômim koat…ôm…®k moatuw…®n moatek net…ôm koat…®m…®s lan. K…ôn n…®m…®s…ôn m…®n k…ômot…ôw…®r, k…ôn narm…®n rat m…®n k…ômotiet elat.\x - \xo 19:12 \xt W…ôk 5:15 \x*   
\p
\v 13 K…ôn net…ôm Isrel neen koatuw…®n ik…®n p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n neen, moat…ôhg-iar…ôp narm…®n rat m…®n e net…ômim, k…ôn net…ôm …ôh k…ômotalkut m…ôm…ô okotol nat …ôh e n…ôrg…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu. K…ôn k…ômoat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm narm…®n rat m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúE n…ôrg…® Iesu, et…ôm kiti…ôh …ôm it…ôm Pol tat…ôn-iar…ôp, otiet.‚Äù   
\p
\v 14 K…ôn e net…ôm k…ômoatol nat …ôh, sep…®n …ôh-ik…®n nen…ôt…® suah kit, n…ôrg…®n u Skefa, u in pris asol ag…®n r…ôha Isrel.  
\v 15 M…ôto narm…®n rat t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEk…®tun suah u Iesu, k…ôn m…®tun m…®n Pol. ?M…ôto it…ômat pah m…®n un?‚Äù  
\v 16 K…ôn suah apon narm…®n rat t…ôtat…®g lan, t…ôm…ôtul maht ilat m…ôr…ôk…®n ilat, m…ôhap-…ôhap r…ôhalat nat…®mnat mapeg r…ôk…®s, k…ôn kotaipi…ôpi…ô …ôm motag…®m e r…ôhan nim…ô k…ômotaig e n…®ta k…ôm…ôhap-…ôhap ilat.  
\v 17 Nian noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel ne net…ôm Kris k…ômot…ôto nat …ôh, k…ômot…ôg…®n p…®k. K…ôn net…ômim komot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu t…ôr p…®k.\x - \xo 19:17 \xt W…ôk 5:11 \x*   
\p
\v 18 K…ôn net…ômim tep…ôt it…ôm kotahat…ôt…ô e Iesu, k…ômot…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm net…ômim nat t…ôrat m…®n it…ôm k…ômoatol.  
\v 19 Neen it…ôm k…ômoat…ôm…®k n…ôr…®k, ilat m…®n k…ômot…ôm…®k naoa m…®n r…ôhalat e nat …ôh moatuwa, moatan-…ôt…®p e n…®gan…ômt…® net…ômim. Nian net…ômim k…ômotafin e n…ômt…® naoa m…®n …ôh, tahmen e fifti-milian fatu ilat rafin.  
\v 20 K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ômaiu iahgin e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn asol r…ôha Uhg…®n.   
\s1 N…ôrg…ôh…ôu…ôn asol kit …ôp…ôh Efesas  
\p
\v 21 K…ôn uaris…®g e nat …ôh, Pol t…®n…ôn e n…®kin m…ôm…ô ot…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn …ôp…ôh Jerusalem, m…ôto otuw…®n-p…ôn Masetonia ne Akaea ik…®n. K…ôn in t…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNian emuw…®n r…ôk…®s Jerusalem, ek…ôike muw…®n m…®n Rom.‚Äù\x - \xo 19:21 \xt W…ôk 23:11; Rom 1:13 \x*  
\v 22 K…ôn in t…ômahl-ip…ôn Timoti ne Erastas it…ôm katuasitu lan, m…ôm…ô okuaup…ôn mian …ôp…ôh Masetonia. M…ôto in otat…®g pit…ôn m…ôs…®n …ôp…ôh ik…®n Esia.   
\p
\v 23 K…ôn e nian …ôh, n…ôrg…ôh…ôu…ôn asol kit t…ôm…ôr …ôp…ôh Efesas o Suat…®p r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.\x - \xo 19:23 \xt 2 Kor 1:8 \x*  
\v 24 Suah kit …ôh-ik…®n it…ôm tatol nat…®mnat e iaen kit kat…ôn m…ôm…ô silfa, n…ôrg…®n u Temetrius. Ik…®n-u net…ômim tep…ôt koat…ôfak k…ôm uhg…®n kit p…ôtan, n…ôrg…®n u Atemis. K…ôn Temetrius tatol narm…® nim…ô m…®n e silfa it…ôm tahmen e nim…ô r…ôha narm…® nat r…ôha Atemis. K…ôn nian tatol-sal…®m-in ilat, matos m…ôni asol ilat r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n.   
\p
\v 25 K…ôn t…ômaun-in r…ôhan net…ômim m…®n ne net…ôm p…®s…®n it…ôm koatol w…ôk kiti…ôh …ôm m…ôm…ô okotuwa kiti…ôh. K…ôn t…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo m…®n, n…ôkot…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô koatol win e m…ôni asol e w…ôk u r…ôhatat.  
\v 26 M…ôto it…ômat n…ômot…ôplan ne mot…ôto m…ôm…ô tahro nulan suah …ôh Pol tat…ôr…ôk…®n net…ômim tep…ôt k…ôn k…®noat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn, s…ôn…ôm…ô e Efesas …ôm, m…ôto iu…ôhk…®r ik…®n m…®n rafin e n…®t…ôn …ôh Esia. In tat…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô uhg…®n m…®n it…ôm net…ômim …ôm koatol e nelm…®lat, s…ôn…ôm…ô uhg…®n m…®n pahrien.  
\v 27 K…ôn roiu …ôh, iu…ôhk…®r …ôm tat…ôr…ôk…®n suat…®p r…ôhatat o nos…ôn m…ôni, k…ôn iu…ôhk…®r …ôm m…®n in tatol m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…ôplan rat nim…ô r…ôha Atemis, u it…ôm in il…®s p…®k. K…ôn namnun, ok…ôm…ô naka n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhan ot…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôrg…®n Atemis it…ôm il…®s p…®k tuwa mol nat …ôpnap…®n …ôm lan. M…ôto ik…®n-u Esia ne ik…®n m…®n rafin, net…ômim koat…ôfak k…ôm uhg…®n u r…ôhatat.‚Äù   
\p
\v 28 Nian k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, n…®kilat t…ômahm…ô t…ômahm…ô, k…ôn …ômun m…®notag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ure e Atemis u Efesas!‚Äù  
\v 29 K…ôn nat …ôh t…ômaiu m…®r…ôfin taon. K…ôn net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômotuwa kiti…ôh motuw…®n kask…ôl…®m et…ôm Masetonia mil …ôh it…ôm katualiw…ôk il…ôhal Pol, n…ôrg…®lau u, Kaeas ne Aristakas. K…ôn k…ômotuw…®n k…ôl…ôh kiuw-p…ôn ilau …ôp…ôh ik…®n nian rafin koatol mitig asol ik…®n.\x - \xo 19:29 \xt W…ôk 20:4; 27:2; Kol 4:10; Flm 24 \x*   
\p
\v 30 K…ôn Pol tolkeike m…ôm…ô otuw…®n m…ôghat k…ôm net…ôm …ôh, m…ôto net…ôm r…ôha Iesu k…ôsoteg…ôhan-in…ôn.  
\v 31 Ne net…ôm-iasol neen r…ôha kaonsel asol …ôp…ôh Esia it…ôm kotolkeike Pol, k…ômotahl-ip…ôn n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm in moat…ôn-i…ôhau …ôskas…®k m…ôm…ô ot…ôsuw…®nen …ôh net…ôm …ôh-ik…®n.   
\p
\v 32 K…ôn ik…®n …ôh, net…ômim koatol wil…®g wil…®g tep…ôt motag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh. Neen koat…ôn nat p…®s…®n, k…ôn neen koat…ôn nat p…®s…®n. M…ôto tep…ôt kot…ôruru m…ôm…ô k…ômotuwa o naka.  
