\v 9 K…ôn et…ôm alu…ô kit, n…ôrg…®n u Iutikas, tat…ôp…ôl…ôh e winta ik…®n. Nian Pol tat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n mat…ôn mat…ôn, k…ôn Iutikas, nap…®l…ôn t…®natos, t…®natiuw n…ôm, …ômun m…ôme e winta m…®s…®-p…ôr muw…®n morin …ôp…ôh l…ôhau e n…ôpt…ôn. K…ôn n…®p…ôg noa nim…ô it…ôm t…ôm…ôme ik…®n, in tatol k…®s…®l lan. K…ôn nian k…ômoteiuaiu motuw…®n, m…ôto t…®n…®m…®s r…ôk…®s.  
\v 10 K…ôn Pol t…ômuw…®n m…®n …ôp…ôh l…ôhau muw…®n m…®sin nul…®n e n…®kal…® et…ôm …ôlue …ôh, k…ôn m…®l…ôs mago-ipa e nelm…®n mil, k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kit…ômat t…ôsahm…ôn. In t…®n…ômeg…ôh m…®n.‚Äù  
\v 11 K…ôn Pol t…ôm…ôr m…®n muw…®n …ôp…ôh il…®s k…ôn mol Nagw…ôn…ôn R…ôha N…ômt…ôtin R…ôha Iesu ilat min ilat, k…ônu motagw…ôn kiti…ôh. K…ôn tat…ôghat m…®n k…ôm ilat m…ôtoarus tian, …ômun tatuw…®n map…ôs ilat.  
\v 12 K…ôn ilat k…ômotit et…ôm alu…ô un motuw…®n latu…ônu. N…®kilat t…ôtagien m…ôto-inu net…ôm alu…ô t…ôm…ômeg…ôh m…®n.   
\s1 K…ômotiet Troas motuw…®n Maelitas  
\p
\v 13 K…ôn Pol t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otaliw…ôk …ôm muw…®n …ôp…ôh e taon …ôh Asos, m…ôto it…®mat ekotuw…®n e nego motuw…®n k…®l…ôs in …ôh-ik…®n. K…ôn it…®mat ekotos nego kaup…ôn kan …ôp…ôh Asos, k…ôn in tuaris…®g muwa.\fig |alt="ship in port and traders" src="HK00214B.TIF" size="col" loc="Act 20:13-14" ref="W…ôk 20:13" \fig*  
