\v 18 Nian k…ômotuwa, t…ôm…ôghat k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômat n…ôkot…®tun r…ôk…®s r…ôhak nol…ôn it…ôm iatol nian emuwa …ôpis ik…®n-u Esia m…ôtoarus-pa roiu.\x - \xo 20:18 \xt W…ôk 18:19‚Äî19:10 \x*  
\v 19 Io iolw…ôk …ôm r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. K…ôn r…ôhak n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn in l…ôhau …ôm. K…ôn nian rafin nahui n…ômt…ôk t…ôtaiu ot…ômat. K…ôn nian rafin etat…®g e nian …ôskas…®k m…®n, m…ôto-inu noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel kotolkeike m…ôm…ô okotohamnu io.  
\v 20 It…ômat n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô o nian iat…ôghat k…ôm it…ômat ne mat…ôg…ôtun it…ômat e n…®ki net…ômim nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm otasitu et…ômat, m…ôs…ôhluaig-in…ôn nat kit ot…ômat, iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô rafin e n…®p…ôgnoa nim…ô m…®n k…ôn ihlu…ô e n…®gamn…ômt…® net…ômim.  
