\v 27 Em…ôn-ip…®n…ô rafin nat…®mnat k…ôm it…ômat it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…®tun.   
\p
\v 28 ‚ÄúOnakoat…ôto w…®r it…ômat. K…ôn net…ômim it…ôm Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…®n…ô e nelm…®t…ômat, on…ôkot…ôk…ôike kehm w…®r ilat e nim…ôfak r…ôha Uhg…®n tahmen e et…ôm r…ôha sipsip it…ôm tatehm w…®r r…ôhan sipsip m…®n. Ilat m…®n …ôh, Uhg…®n t…ômos-n…ômt…®n ilat e n…®ta n…ôt…®n.\f + \fr 20:28 \ft Suat…®p kit m…®n o n…ôuhlin…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u ‚Äún…®ta n…ôt…®n‚Äù in tol min-nulan: ‚Äún…®tan at…®p.‚Äù\f*\x - \xo 20:28 \xt 1 Tim 4:16; 1 Pita 5:2-4 \x*  
\v 29 En…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô nian ekiet r…ôk…®s et…ômat, net…ômim neen it…ôm kotahmen e kuri iarup…®n m…®n okotuwa m…ôm…ô okotus it…ômat net…ômim r…ôha Iesu.\x - \xo 20:29 \xt Mat 7:15; Jon 10:12 \x*  
