\v 3 M…ôto Pol t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Uhg…®n otol mihin m…®n lam! Ik nakahmen e nim…ô it…ôm k…ômol pen lan t…ôru…ôn p…®k …ôm ihlu…ô, m…ôto tamk…®m…®k …ôp…ôh im…ô. ?Tahro nat…ôp…ôl…ôh ik…®n-u m…ôtakil io e Lou r…ôhatat, m…ôto ik n…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô kit otem io? Ik n…®n…ôtg…ôhl r…ôk…®s Lou …ôh.‚Äù\x - \xo 23:3 \xt Mat 23:27 \x*   
