\v 27 Suah u, noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…®notask…ôl…®m r…ôk…®s, k…ôn iu…ôhk…®r kotohamnu. M…ôto io em…ôto m…ôm…ô in et…ôm Rom, k…ôn ekuw…®n it…®mat r…ôhak mopael m…®n k…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s olat.\x - \xo 23:27 \xt W…ôk 21:30-33; 22:25-27 \x*  
