\v 35 in t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNian net…ômim okotuwa k…ôn-iar…ôp nat…®mnat it…ôm koat…ôplan-p…ôn …ôh lam, io ek…ôn kot ot…ôp…ôl…ôh o n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn u r…ôham, k…ôn io ekakil.‚Äù K…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm r…ôhan mopael m…®n m…ôm…ô okot…®l…ôs-ip…ôn Pol e nim…ô r…ôha kapman r…ôha Rom it…ôm Kig Herot Asol t…ômil…ôk…®n aup…ôn, motask…ôl…®m …ôh-ik…®n.   
\c 24  
\s1 Pol t…ôm…ôtul aup…ôn e Filiks e kot  
\m
\v 1 Nian faif t…®nuw…®n r…ôk…®s, k…ôn pris asol ag…®n, n…ôrg…®n u Ananaeas, t…ômuw…®n Sisaria ilat net…ôm-iasol m…®n neen r…ôha Isrel ne ienat…®g e lou,\f + \fr 24:1 \ft Ienat…®g e lou in suah kit it…ôm t…®tun w…®r lou mat…ôghat e kot.\f* n…ôrg…®n u Tetalas. Nian k…ômotiet-pa, k…ôn motuw…®n k…ôtul e n…®gan…ômt…® Filiks k…ôn mot…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm n…®kilat t…ôht m…ôm…ô Pol t…ômol t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn.  
\v 2 K…ôn k…ômotaun-in Pol m…ôm…ô otuwa im…ô e n…ôghat…ôn, k…ôn Tetalas tat…ôn-ip…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhalat k…ôm Filiks m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm-iasol. Ekot…®siai-in p…®k ik m…ôto-inu ik il…®s pahrien. K…ôn nol…ôn r…ôham o n…ôm…®k…ôn it…®mat in tat…ôtuat…®p w…®r. Imat…®mat ik…®n t…ôm…ôm…ôlinu nuw…ôh r…ôk…®s m…ôtoarus-pa u-roiu. K…ôn ik n…ôm…ôg-…ôtuat…®p-in r…ôk…®s nol…ôn u ik…®n-u m…ôm…ô otol n…ômeg…ôh…ôn ne nat…®g…ôn r…ôhat…®mat t…ôw…®r.  
\v 3 K…ôn nian rafin kitat koat…ôto t…ôw…®r o nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh, k…ôn ekot…ônwiwi p…®k ik ron.  
\v 4 Esotolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô ekask…ôl…®m p…®k ik, m…ôto ek…ôtap…ôh ron ik m…ôm…ô onakas…ôkitun it…®mat m…ôt…ôl…®g-in w…®r-tu n…ôghat…ôn …ôku…ôk…®r u r…ôhat…®mat.   
\p
\v 5 ‚ÄúIt…®mat emot…ôplan r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô suah …ôh in et…ôm t…ôrat kit. In n…ôuk…ôt…® n…ôrat…ôn tep…ôt e ik…®n m…®n e n…®t…ôn m…®n. In tatol it…®mat net…ôm Isrel ekoat…ôrg…ôh…ôu p…®k, k…ôn et…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm koatuaris…®g-in suah ilouin et…ôm Nasaret.\x - \xo 24:5 \xt W…ôk 17:6 \x*  
\v 6 K…ôn in m…ôtalkut m…ôm…ô otol Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n tamk…®m…®k e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôn ekotask…ôl…®m.\f + \fr 24:6 \ft E kopi oas m…®n neen r…ôha Niutesteman it…ôm k…ôm…ôte e n…ôghat…ôn Kris aup…ôn, n…ôghat…ôn p…®s…®n kit m…®n …ôh-ik…®n it…ôm tat…®lp…®n n…ôghat…ôn u mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…ôn emot…ôn m…ôm…ô ekot…ôtu-p…ôn n…ôghat…ôn kit lan e kot e nol…ôn r…ôha Lou r…ôhat…®mat. 7 M…ôto Lisias it…ôm t…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e mopael m…®n, t…ôm…®l…ôs n…ôlug…® n…ôn…ôn r…ôhat…®mat, k…ôn ilat r…ôhan net…ômim k…ômoteuw r…ôk…®s m…®n suah u ot…®mat. 8 K…ôn m…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôn…ôn kit m…ôm…ô net…ômim it…ôm koat…ôplan-p…ôn n…ôrat…ôn kit e suah u, ot…ôk…ôike muwa m…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm ik.‚Äù\f*\x - \xo 24:6 \xt W…ôk 21:28-30 \x*  
