\v 24 K…ôn uaris…®g e nian neen, Filiks t…ômit r…ôhan p…ôtan Trusila muwa u noanol kit r…ôha Isrel. K…ôn Filiks t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô okotit Pol motuwa-tu t…ôtul aup…ôn in. K…ôn nian Pol t…ômuwa, k…ôn mat…ôghat k…ôm ilau mat…ôn-ip…ôn nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn e Kristo Iesu.  
