\v 25 M…ôto io es…ôplan…ôn nat t…ôrat kit lan ne, it…ôm ekol nalp…®n…ôn k…ôm in e n…®m…®s…ôn. M…ôto nian in t…ôm…ôtap…ôh m…ôm…ô otuw…®n m…ôplan Sisa …ôp…ôh Rom, k…ôn n…®kik t…ôht m…ôm…ô ekeg…ôhan-in.  
